er Spinal Cord Injury. Neuroscience (178): 33-44</li>\n	<li>\n		Guzm&aacute;n MS., Navarro X., Casas C. (2009). Selective Sigma Receptor Agonist PRE084 Promotes Neuroprotection and Neurite Elongation Through PKC Signaling on Motoneurons. Neuroscience (162): 31-38</li>\n	<li>\n		Penas C., Casas C., Robert I., For&eacute;s J., Navarro X. (2009) Cytoskeletal and activity-related changes in spinal motoneurons after root avulsion. J &nbsp;Neurotrauma 26(5): 763-779</li>\n	<li>\n		Guzm&aacute;n-Lenis M.,&nbsp; Navarro X., Casas C (2009) Drug screening for neuroprotection against spinal cord excitotoxic damage in an organotypic-based model. Restorative Neurological Neuroscience ( 27): 335-349</li>\n	<li>\n		Penas C., Guzm&aacute;n-Lenis M., Verd&uacute; E., For&eacute;s J., Navarro X., Casas C (2007). Spinal Cord Injury Induces Endoplasmic Reticulum Stress with Different Cell-Type Dependent Response J NEUROCHEMISTRY&nbsp; (102): 1242-1255</li>\n</ul>\n','<p>\n	<font color=\"#666666\" face=\"Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px;\">&nbsp;</span></font></p>\n<table height=\"25\" width=\"40\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n				<a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0002-2273-6321 \" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/orcid.png\" style=\"width: 25px; height: 25px;\" /></a></td>\n			<td>\n				<a href=\"http://www.researcherid.com/ProfileView.action?SID=Q2cBildMheG8C2OWlJL&amp;returnCode=ROUTER.Success&amp;queryString=KG0UuZjN5WnWRkoEY6n%2FnddSewtPe7WsIZHlj85OBdw%3D&amp;SrcApp=CR&amp;Init=Yes\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/RID.jpg\" style=\"width: 25px; height: 25px;\" /></a></td>\n			<td>\n				<a href=\"http://www.scopus.com/authid/detail.url?authorId=7006142795\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/scopus.jpg\" style=\"width: 25px; height: 25px;\" /></a></td>\n			<td>\n				<a href=\"http://www.researchgate.net/profile/Caty_Casas\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images