 />\n	Guillermo Garc&iacute;a-Alias<br />\n	<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Catala/profile.php?id=88\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Ruben L&oacute;pez-Vales</span></a><br />\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Catala/profile.php?id=135\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Esther Udina</span></a><br />\n	<strong>Professors associats:</strong><br />\n	Jordi Bruna<br />\n	Roser Velasco<br />\n	Jorge J. Vilches<br />\n	<strong>Investigadors&nbsp;<br />\n	postdoctorals</strong>:<br />\n	<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Castellano/profile.php?id=54\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Jaume Del Valle</span></a><br />\n	Ignacio Delgado<br />\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> Joaquim Hern&aacute;ndez</span><br />\n	<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Catala/profile.php?id=79\">Mireia Herrando</a><br />\n	<strong>Investigadors<br />\n	predoctorals</strong>:<br />\n	Jes&uacute;s Amo<br />\n	Ariadna Arbat<br />\n	Isaac Francos<br />\n	Tatiana Leiva<br />\n	V&iacute;ctor L&oacute;pez<br />\n	Clara L&oacute;pez<br />\n	Anna Mart&iacute;nez<br />\n	Guillem M&ograve;dol<br />\n	Natalia de la Oliva<br />\n	Maria Puigdom&egrave;nech<br />\n	David Romeo<br />\n	Alba Sanchez<br />\n	Irene Sanchez<br />\n	Daniel Santos<br />\n	<strong>Investigadors col.laboradors:</strong><br />\n	Jordi Badia<br />\n	Joaquim For&eacute;s<br />\n	<strong>T&egrave;cnics</strong>:<br />\n	Israel Blasco<br />\n	M&oacute;nica Espejo<br />\n	J&egrave;sica Jaramillo</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<br />\n	<br />\n	<span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>OBJECTIUS ESTRAT&Egrave;GICS</strong></span><br />\n	<br />\n	El Grup de Neuroplasticitat i Regeneraci&oacute; &eacute;s un grup de recerca multidisciplinari que investiga en la regeneraci&oacute; i recuperaci&oacute; funcional despr&eacute;s de lesions dels nervis perif&egrave;rics i de la medul&middot;la espinal i en malalties neurodegeneratives. Els membres del grup tenen experi&egrave;ncies combinades en microcirurgia, neurofisiologia, morfologia, cultuis cel&middot;lulars, neurobiologia molecular i bioelectr&ograve;nica. Els projectes d&rsquo;investigaci&oacute; desenvolupats durant els darrrers anys han tractat sobre: regeneraci&oacute; i reinnervaci&oacute; despr&eacute;s de lesions de nervis i d&rsquo;arrels espinals, empelts artificials biocompatibles, trasplants glials per la reparaci&oacute; de lesions en el sistema nervi&oacute;s perif&egrave;ric i central, electrodes neurals per la interf&iacute;cie amb el sistema nervi&oacute;s lesionat. El grup t&eacute; establerta recerca cooperativa en neuroci&egrave;ncia cl&iacute;nica, particularment sobre noves ter&agrave;pies reparatives de nervis amb l&rsquo;Hospital Clinic de Barcelona, i sobre modulaci&oacute; de la plasticitat neural en lesions cerebrals i medul&middot;lars amb l&rsquo;Institut Guttmann de Neurorehabilitaci&oacute;.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<br />\n	<span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>PRINCIPALS L&Iacute;NIES D&#39;INVESTIGACI&Oacute;</strong></span><br />\n	<br />\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Regeneraci&oacute; i reinnervaci&oacute; despr&eacute;s de lesions de nervis perif&egrave;rics.<br />\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Fisiopatologia i tractament del dolor neurop&agrave;tic.<br />\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Avaluaci&oacute; i fisiopatologia de neuropaties perif&egrave;riques.<br />\n	&bull; Mecanismes moleculars i cel.lulars en la degeneraci&oacute; de motoneurones.<br />\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Desenvolupament d&rsquo;empelts nerviosos biocompatibles.<br />\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; Trasplantament de c&egrave;l.lules glials i progenitores per la reparaci&oacute; de lesions de medul.la espinal.<br />\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Modulaci&oacute; de la resposta inflamat&ograve;ria en lesions del SNC.<br />\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; Avaluaci&oacute; d&rsquo;interf&iacute;cies neurals i neuropr&ograve;tesis per la rehabilitaci&oacute; del sistema nervi&oacute;s lesionat.&nbsp;<br />\n	<br />\n	&nbsp;<br />\n	<span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong> PROJECTES D&#39;INVESTIGACI&Oacute; FINAN&Ccedil;ATS EN ELS DARRERS 5 ANYS </strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; Projecte d&#39;Investigaci&oacute; PI060201, <em>Fondo de Investigaci&oacute;n Sanitaria, Inst Salud Carlos III</em>, 2007-09. &ldquo;Transplantes gliales combinados con neuroprotecci&oacute;n y restituci&oacute;n neuronal para la reparaci&oacute;n de lesiones de ra&iacute;ces espinales&rdquo;.<br />\n	&bull;&nbsp; Projecte d&#39;Investigaci&oacute; SAF2006-08682, <em>Ministerio de Educaci&oacute;n y Ciencia,</em> 2007-09. &ldquo;Terapia f&aacute;rmaco-celular para la reparaci&oacute;n de la m&eacute;dula espinal lesionada&rdquo;.<br />\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; Projecte d&#39;Investigaci&oacute; 070210, <em>Fundaci&oacute; La Marat&oacute;TV3,</em> 2008-2010. &quot;Trasplantaments cel.lulars i tractament farmacol&ograve;gic per a redu&iuml;r el dolor neurop&agrave;tic a lesions de la m&egrave;dula espinal.&quot;<br />\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; Grup membre del <em>Centro de Investigaci&oacute;n Biom&eacute;dica en Red sobre Enfermedades Neurodegenerativas (CIBERNED)</em>, Inst Salud Carlos III, 2008-2014. CB06/05/1105.<br />\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Grup de la <em>Red de Terapia Celular</em> RD06/0010/1004, <em>Instituto de Salud Carlos III,</em> 2008-2012.<br />\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; Projecte d&#39;Investigaci&oacute; FP7 ICT-224012, Comission of the European Communities, 2008-2012. &ldquo;Transverse, Intrafascicular Multichannel Electrode system for induction of sensation and treatment of phantom limb pain in amputees (TIME)&rdquo;.<br />\n	&bull;&nbsp; Marie Curie Initial Training Network, FP7- MC-214003-2, European Commission, 2008-2012. &ldquo;Axonal regeneration, plasticity and stem cells (AXREGEN)&rdquo;.<br />\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; Projecte d&#39;Investigaci&oacute; PI080598, <em>Fondo de Investigaci&oacute;n Sanitaria, Inst Salud Carlos III</em>, 2008-10. &ldquo;Efectos de la estimulaci&oacute;n el&eacute;ctrica del nervio perif&eacute;rico sobre la plasticidad de los circuitos espinales y la regeneraci&oacute;n axonal despu&eacute;s de lesiones nerviosas o medulares&rdquo;.<br />\n	&bull;&nbsp; Ajuda a la recerca, <em>Fundaci&oacute;n Mapfre</em>, 2009. &ldquo;Administraci&oacute;n de AB-cristalina como terapia protectora de las lesiones de la m&eacute;dula espinal&rdquo;.<br />\n	&bull;&nbsp; Projecte d&#39;Investigaci&oacute; WFL-SE-008/09, <em>Wings for Life Foundation</em>, 2009-10. &ldquo;Role of lysophosphatidic acid in the pathophysiology of spinal cord injury&rdquo;.<br />\n	&bull;&nbsp; Projecte d&#39;Investigaci&oacute; SAF2009-12495, <em>Ministerio de Ciencia e Innovacion</em>, 2010-12. &ldquo;Respuesta medular al trasplante de glia envolvente y de c&eacute;lulas estromales de la m&eacute;dula &oacute;sea: estudios in vitro e in vivo&rdquo;.<br />\n	&bull; Projecte d&#39;Investigaci&oacute; PIRG05-GA-2009-249274, <em>Marie-Curie International Reintegration Grant</em>, European Commission FP7, 2010-2014. &ldquo;Role of lysophosphatidic acid in the pathophysiology of spinal cord injury (ROLPASCI)&rdquo;.<br />\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; Bolsas de Doutoramento e P&oacute;s-Doutoramento 2011, <em>Funda&ccedil;&atilde;o para a Ci&ecirc;ncia e a Tecnologia, Minist&eacute;rio da Ci&ecirc;ncia, Tecnologia e Ensino Superior de Portugal</em>, 2011-2013. &ldquo;Dissecting the mechanisms of microglia response, determinants and biomarkers in Amyotrophic Lateral Sclerosis&rdquo;.<br />\n	&bull;&nbsp; Projecte d&#39;Investigaci&oacute; SAF2010-17851, <em>Ministerio de Ciencia e Innovacion</em>, 2011-13. &ldquo;Activaci&oacute;n de los programas de resoluci&oacute;n de la inflamaci&oacute;n como nueva terapia neuroprotectora para tratar las lesiones agudas de la m&eacute;dula espinal&rdquo;.<br />\n	&bull;&nbsp; Projecte d&#39;Investigaci&oacute; IRP Research Grant P123, <em>International Foundation for Research in Paraplegia</em>, 2011-12. &ldquo;Lysopho