ebro normal, qu&eacute; ocurre cuando enferma, y c&oacute;mo se cura. Exploramos todos los niveles de la organizaci&oacute;n biol&oacute;gica desde la interacci&oacute;n de mol&eacute;culas al comportamiento usando para ello cultivos celulares, modelos animales y pacientes. Nuestro objetivo final es desarrollar nuevas terapias celulares, moleculares, gen&eacute;ticas para el tratamiento de patolog&iacute;as cerebrales.</p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n				&nbsp;</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n				&nbsp;</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n',0,1,1),(345,51,0,'INc en cifras','<p>\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/INC NUMBERS.jpg\" style=\"width: 450px; height: 356px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	Consulta la <u><strong><a href=\"https://issuu.com/web.inc/docs/interior_incuab_annual_reports_2012\" target=\"_blank\">memoria del Instituto</a></strong></u><strong><a href=\"https://issuu.com/web.inc/docs/interior_incuab_annual_reports_2012\" target=\"_blank\"> </a></strong>para acceder a toda la informaci&oacute;n.</p>\n',1,1,1),(346,51,0,'Organización','<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"5\" style=\"text-align: left; width: 100%;\" width=\"100%\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"width: 118px;\">\n				<p>\n					&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"width: 198px;\">\n				<p>\n					<strong>E-mail</strong></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"width: 111px;\">\n				<p>\n					<strong>Tel&eacute;fono</strong></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n				<p>\n					<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(165, 42, 42);\">Director:</span></strong></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n				&nbsp;</td>\n			<td>\n				<p>\n					&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">\n				<p>\n					Ignacio Morgado</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n				<p>\n					<a href=\"mailto:direccio.inc@uab.cat\">direccio.inc@uab.cat</a></p>\n		