;n del sistema glutamat&eacute;rgico glial (glutamina sintetasa y GLAST) por la activaci&oacute;n de los trasportadores de glutamato de alta afinidad</strong><br />\n	Tesi doctoral: Daniel Alejandro Martinez Quintero<br />\n	Director/s: Jos&eacute; Aguilera i Arturo Ortega Soto</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<strong>T&iacute;tol: Electrophysiological biomarkers for the study of new therapeutic strategies for motoneuron disease</strong><br />\n	Tesi doctoral: Renzo Mancuso<br />\n	Director: Xavier Navarro</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<strong>T&iacute;tol: Effects of neonatal Allopregnanolone alteration levels on adult behavior-Role of dorsal hippocampus</strong><br />\n	Tesi doctoral: Laura M&ograve;dol Vidal<br />\n	Director/s: Marc Pallar&egrave;s/Sonia Darbra</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<strong>T&iacute;tol: Especificidad de las poblaciones neuronales activadas en respuesta a distintos est&iacute;mulos estresantes emocionales</strong><br />\n	Tesi doctoral: Ignacio Mar&iacute;n Blasco<br />\n	Director: Antonio Armario</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<strong>T&iacute;tol: Neuroprotecci&oacute; en la isqu&egrave;mia cerebral per inhibici&oacute; de la senyalitzaci&oacute; mediada pels receptors de mort</strong><br />\n	Tesi doctoral: Guillem Sanchez Opazo<br />\n	Director: Jos&eacute; Rodr&iacute;guez &Aacute;lvarez</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<strong>T&iacute;tol: Papel del coactivador transcripcional CRTCI en sinapsis en modelos de la enfermedad de Alzheimer</strong><br />\n	Tesi doctoral: Meng Cheng<br />\n	Director: Carles A. Saura</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<strong>T&iacute;tol: Desregulations of A-Kinase anchoring proteins (AKAPs) and microRNAs (miRNAs) in Alzheimer&#39;s disease: searching for biomarkers for early diagnosis non-invasive</strong><br />\n	Tesi doctoral: Wenwen Cheng<br />\n	Director: Jos&eacute; Rodr&iacute;guez &Aacute;lvarez</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	