i per a la Igualtat de la UAB</span></span></u></p>\n<p>\n	<u><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><a href=\"http://www.fwis.fr/en/home\" target=\"_blank\">For Women in Science. Fundaci&oacute; L&rsquo;Oreal-UNESCO</a></span></span></u></p>\n<p>\n	<u><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><a href=\"http://www.idi.mineco.gob.es/portal/site/MICINN/menuitem.26172fcf4eb029fa6ec7da6901432ea0/?vgnextoid=e218c5aa16493210VgnVCM1000001d04140aRCRD\" target=\"_blank\">Unidad de Mujeres y Ciencia- UMYC (MINECO)</a></span></span></u></p>\n<p>\n	<u><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><a href=\"http://ec.europa.eu/research/science-society/document_library/pdf_06/vademecum_gender_h2020.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Gender Equality in Horizon 2020</a></span></span></u></p>\n<p>\n	<u><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><a href=\"http://www.sfn.org/careers-and-training/women-in-neuroscience\" target=\"_blank\">Women in Neuroscience- SfN</a></span></span></u></p>\n<p>\n	<u><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><a href=\"http://genderedinnovations.stanford.edu/methods/sex.html\" target=\"_blank\">Gendered innovations in Science, Health and Medicine</a></span></span></u></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n',87,2,1),(681,86,0,'Gender policies','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	The<em> Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</em> is strongly committed to gender equality. To promote it, has initiated a process of developing a <strong>Gender Equality Plan</strong>, which will be available soon.<br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Female neuroscientist of the month</strong></span></u></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	During this 2016-2017 course we want