http://ibro.info/\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"84\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/IBRO.jpg\" width=\"81\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<em><strong>Sociedad Espa&ntilde;ola de Bioqu&iacute;mica y Biolog&iacute;a Molecular:</strong></em></p>\n<p>\n	<a href=\"http://www.sebbm.es/\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"55\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/SEBBM.jpg\" width=\"115\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"gt-src-tools\">\n	<div id=\"gt-src-tools-l\">\n		<div id=\"gt-input-tool\" style=\"display: inline-block;\">\n			<div id=\"itamenu\">\n				&nbsp;</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"almost_half_cell\" id=\"gt-res-content\">\n	<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"zoom:1\">\n		&nbsp;</div>\n	<br />\n	<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"zoom:1\">\n		&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n',87,2,2),(698,30,0,'Laboratoris tècnics del INc',NULL,7,0,0),(699,30,0,'Cultius cel·lulars','<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<p>\n		El laboratori de cultius cel&middot;lulars de l&rsquo;Inc &eacute;s un laboratori destinat a facilitar els recursos necessaris per treballar amb l&iacute;nies cel&middot;lulars i cultius primaris per a la seva posterior avaluaci&oacute; qualitativa i quantitativa mitjan&ccedil;ant diferents t&egrave;cniques.</p>\n	<p>\n		Per aix&ograve;, el laboratori compta amb personal t&egrave;cnic qualificat i experimentat, aix&iacute; com amb equips amb diverses prestacions.</p>\n	<p>\n		Aquest laboratori i equips estan a disposici&oacute; dels grups de l&rsquo;INc, investigadors de la UAB i institucions p&uacute;bliques i privades.</p>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n		<tbody>\n			<tr>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/DSC00244.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/gfap_5.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 114px;\" /></td>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/DSC00260.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 114px;\" /></td>\n			</tr>\n		</tbody>\n	</table>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Les tasques que realitzen els t&egrave;cnics de l&rsquo;INc s&oacute;n:&nbsp;</strong></span></u></p>\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n			Manteniment i coordinaci&oacute; de l&#39;&uacute;s d&#39;aparells comuns de l&rsquo;INc de la seva especialitat.</li>\n		<li>\n			Formaci&oacute; en t&egrave;cniques especialitzades desenvolupades pel t&egrave;cnic especialista.</li>\n		<li>\n			Formaci&oacute; obligat&ograve;ria per a usuaris en r&egrave;gim d&#39;autoservei.</li>\n		<li>\n			Realitzaci&oacute; de procediments experimentals per part del t&egrave;cnic especialista.</li>\n	</ul>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<u><a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(579,1);\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">T&egrave;cniques ofertades</span></a></u></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<p>\n		<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Equipament</strong></span></u></p>\n	<p>\n		Actualment el laboratori compta amb tres sales de cultius cel&middot;lulars, una destinada al treball amb l&iacute;nies cel&middot;lulars, altra per cultius primaris i una tercera d&rsquo;us per qualsevol processament dels anteriors. A m&eacute;s a m&eacute;s, aquests laboratoris compten amb equips que tamb&eacute; estan a disposici&oacute; de l&rsquo;Inc, que encara que no estiguin situats als laboratoris de cultius, son necessaris per portar a terme el treball en cultius.</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\n		<u><a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(567,1);\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> M2/103. Sala de l&iacute;nies cel&middot;lulars</span></a></u></p>\n	<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\n		<u><a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(568,1);\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">M2/104. Sala mixta</span></a></u></p>\n	<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\n		<u><a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(569,1);\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">M2/130.2. Sala de cultius primaris</span></a></u></p>\n	<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\n		<u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/equipament%20gral%20totes%20les%20sales.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Equips generals a totes les sales</span></a></u></p>\n	<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\n		<u><a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(570,1);\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Equips associats a cultius</span></a></u></p>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<p>\n		<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Condicions generals</strong></span></u></p>\n	<p>\n		Els membres de l&rsquo;INc tindran prefer&egrave;ncia sobre els no membres i dins d&#39;aquests grups, els que no hagin utilitzat anteriorment els laboratoris o equips comuns tindran prefer&egrave;ncia respecte als que ho hagin fet recentment. Un altre par&agrave;metre important ser&agrave; l&#39;ordre de recepci&oacute; de peticions i la possibilitat del t&egrave;cnic d&rsquo;intercalar-les amb altres sol&bull;licituds.</p>\n	<p>\n		<br />\n		<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Tarifes&nbsp; </strong></span></u></p>\n	<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/161123_Proposta%20Tarifes%202017_DEF%20(2)(1).pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Tarifes&nbsp;2017&nbsp;</u></a><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/NOU.gif\" style=\"width: 26px; height: 13px;\" /></strong></u></span><br />\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n		<tbody>\n			<tr>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Ra0_25dbx20xmerge.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 111px;\" /></td>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/DSC00238.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 111px;\" /></td>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/DSC00254.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 111px;\" /></td>\n			</tr>\n		</tbody>\n	</table>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		Per a m&eacute;s informaci&oacute; i comandes contactar amb:</p>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Catala/profile.php?id=77\"><strong>Cristina Guti&eacute;rrez Salvador</strong></a><br />\n	Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Unitat de Bioqu&iacute;mica i Biolog&iacute;a Molecular</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Facultat de Medicina</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"mailto:inc.cultius@uab.es \"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">inc.cultius@uab.es&nbsp;</span></a></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Tel: 935814828</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Fax: 935811573</div>\n',8,1,0),(700,30,0,'Histologia','<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<p>\n		El Laboratori d&rsquo;Histologia de l&rsquo;INc &eacute;s un laboratori destinat a facilitar el processament de diferents tipus de mostres per a la seva posterior avaluaci&oacute; qualitativa i quantitativa mitjan&ccedil;ant microsc&ograve;pia &ograve;ptica i/o confocal.</p>\n	<p>\n		Per aix&ograve;, el laboratori compta amb personal t&egrave;cnic qualificat i experimentat, aix&iacute; com amb equips amb moltes prestacions (veure llistat m&eacute;s avall).</p>\n	<p>\n		Aquest laboratori i equips estan a disposici&oacute; dels grups de l&rsquo;INc, investigadors de la UAB i institucions p&uacute;bliques i privades.</p>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<table cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n		<tbody>\n			<tr>\n				<td>\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/Criotomia_medul_la_ratoli.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n				<td>\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/hist2.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n			</tr>\n		</tbody>\n	</table>\n	<p>\n		<br />\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Les tasques que realitzen els t&egrave;cnics de l&rsquo;INc s&oacute;n:&nbsp;</strong></span></u></p>\n</div>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		Manteniment i coordinaci&oacute; de l&#39;&uacute;s d&#39;aparells comuns de l&rsquo;INc de la seva especialitat.</li>\n	<li>\n		Formaci&oacute; en t&egrave;cniques especialitzades desenvolupades pel t&egrave;cnic especialista.</li>\n	<li>\n		Formaci&oacute; obligat&ograve;ria per a usuaris en r&egrave;gim d&#39;autoservei.</li>\n	<li>\n		Realitzaci&oacute; de procediments experimentals per part del t&egrave;cnic especialista.</li>\n</ul>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n		<p>\n			<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>T&egrave;cniques que s&#39;ofereixen:</strong></span></u></p>\n		<ul>\n			<li>\n				<p>\n					Processament histol&ograve;gic d&rsquo;inclusi&oacute; en parafina (nom&eacute;s per part del t&egrave;cnic especialista)</p>\n			</li>\n		</ul>\n		<p>\n			<span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -</span><u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/TarifasparafinaAll.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Tarifes material inclusi&oacute;</span></a></u></p>\n		<p>\n			<span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -</span><u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/CatTISSUE%20PROCESSOR.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Tissue processor</span></a></u></p>\n		<p>\n			<span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -</span><u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/CatPARAFFIN%20EMBEDDING%20STATION.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Paraffine embeding station</span></a></u></p>\n		<ul>\n			<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n				<p>\n					Processament histol&ograve;gic per a congelaci&oacute;</p>\n			</li>\n			<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n				<p>\n					Microtomia: <u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/CatLEICA%20MICROTOME%20RM%202255.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">LEICA MICROTOME RM 2255 </span></a></u></p>\n			</li>\n			<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n				<p>\n					Criotomia: <u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/CatSME%20CRYOTOME%20THERMO.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">SME CRYOTOME THERMO</span></a></u>&nbsp; i <u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/CatCRYOSTAT%20LEICA%20CM3050%20S.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">CRYOSTAT LEICA CM3050S</span></a></u></p>\n			</li>\n			<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n				<p>\n					Seccions amb vibr&agrave;tom: <u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/CatLEICA%20VT%201000S.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">LEICA VT 1000S </span></a></u></p>\n			</li>\n			<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n				<p>\n					Coloracions (Hematoxilina-eosina, blau de toluidina, violeta de cresil, Hoechst), t&egrave;cniques histoqu&iacute;miques i immunohistoqu&iacute;miques / immunofluoresc&egrave;ncia: <u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/CatDAKO%20AUTOSTAINER.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">DAKO AUTOSTAINER</span></a></u>&nbsp; i <u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/GENERAL%20LAB%20EQUIPMENT%20CATALA.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">GENERAL LAB EQUIPMENT </span></a></u></p>\n			</li>\n			<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n				<p>\n					Suport en an&agrave;lisi multiplex:<u> <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/CatMAGPIX.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">MAGPIX </span></a></u></p>\n			</li>\n		</ul>\n	</div>\n	<br />\n	<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Condicions generals</strong></span></u></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<p>\n		Els membres de l&rsquo;INc tindran prefer&egrave;ncia sobre els no membres i dins d&#39;aquests grups, els que no hagin utilitzat anteriorment els laboratoris o equips comuns tindran prefer&egrave;ncia respecte als que ho hagin fet recentment. Un altre par&agrave;metre important ser&agrave; l&#39;ordre de recepci&oacute; de peticions i la possibilitat del t&egrave;cnic d&rsquo;intercalar-les amb altres sol&bull;licituds.</p>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Tarifes</strong></span></u></p>\n	<p>\n		<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/161123_Proposta%20Tarifes%202017_DEF%20(2)(1).pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Tarifes 2017&nbsp;</u></a><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/NOU.gif\" style=\"width: 26px; height: 13px;\" /></strong></u></span></p>\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n		&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<span style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</span><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/hist1.JPG\" style=\"width: 25%;\" /><span style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</span></div>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<br />\n	Per a m&eacute;s informaci&oacute; i comandes contactar amb:</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Catala/profile.php?id=40\"><strong>Mar Castillo Ruiz</strong></a></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Lab M1/109-M1/110. Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Torre M-1ra planta&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"mailto:inc.histologia@uab.cat\">inc.histologia@uab.cat&nbsp;</a></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Tel: 935814728</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Fax:935814152</div>\n',9,1,0),(701,30,0,'Microscòpia','<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<p>\n		El laboratori de Microsc&ograve;pia de l&rsquo;INc &eacute;s un laboratori destinat a facilitar l&rsquo;observaci&oacute; de diferents tipus de mostres, per tal de poder avaluar-les qualitativa i quantitativament.</p>\n	<p>\n		Aquest laboratori, localitzat a la M1-147 de la Facultat de Medicina de la UAB, est&agrave; a disposici&oacute; dels grups de l&rsquo;INc, investigadors de la UAB i institucions p&uacute;bliques i privades.</p>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Tasques que realitzen els t&egrave;cnics del Laboratori de Microsc&ograve;pia </strong></span></u></p>\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n			Manteniment i coordinaci&oacute; de l&#39;&uacute;s dels diferents microscopis propis del Laboratori de Microsc&ograve;pia.</li>\n		<li>\n			Suport t&egrave;cnic en l&rsquo;&uacute;s dels microscopis i softwares de processament d&rsquo;imatge (ImageJ, Metamorph) per a personal no format, ja sigui amb els propis equips de l&rsquo;INc o en equips fora d&rsquo;aquest, propis de la UAB.</li>\n		<li>\n			Formaci&oacute; obligat&ograve;ria per a usuaris en r&egrave;gim d&#39;autoservei.</li>\n		<li>\n			Realitzaci&oacute; de procediments experimentals per part del t&egrave;cnic especialista.</li>\n	</ul>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Equips</strong></span></u></p>\n	<p>\n		Permeten fer estudis de imatge 3D, fluoresc&egrave;ncia m&uacute;ltiple i an&agrave;lisi de col&middot;localitzaci&oacute;, captaci&oacute; d&rsquo;imatge <em>in vivo</em>, estudis de calci intracel&middot;lular, de pH, de potencial de membrana, entre altres.</p>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n		<tbody>\n			<tr>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/Amaia.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" height=\"131\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/8DIV_NGCP_G-MAP_R-GFAP_20x_01_3D.jpg\" width=\"195\" /></td>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/Carlos-Barcia_2.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n			</tr>\n		</tbody>\n	</table>\n	<p>\n		<u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/150309_Fitxa%20Zeiss%20LSM700_CAT.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Microscopi de rastreig l&agrave;ser confocal (Zeiss LSM 700): M1-147</span></a></u></p>\n	<p>\n		<a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(655,1);\"><br />\n		<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></a></p>\n	<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n		<tbody>\n			<tr>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/cerebel_40x_01.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" height=\"120\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/Objs-Eclipse-90i.jpg\" width=\"159\" /></td>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/150205_Marian-Baltrons-90i.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n			</tr>\n		</tbody>\n	</table>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<u><a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(655,1);\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Microscopis &ograve;ptics d&#39;epifluoresc&egrave;ncia Nikon Eclipse 90i i 80i: M1-147</span></a></u></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(656,1);\"><br />\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></a></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n		<tbody>\n			<tr>\n				<td style=\"width: 50%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/Roser_01.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n				<td>\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/Roser_03.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n			</tr>\n		</tbody>\n	</table>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<u><a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(656,1);\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Microscopis &ograve;ptics d&#39;epifluoresc&egrave;ncia Nikon Eclipse TE2000-E i TE2000-U: M2-129.1</span></a></u></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Marcadors</strong></span><strong> </strong></u></p>\n	<p>\n		Disposem d&rsquo;una &agrave;mplia gamma de marcadors:<u><a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/150309_llistat%20abs%20i%20marcadors%20web_CAT.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"> <span style=\"color:#000000;\">anticossos secundaris, estreptavidines i marcadors directes de nucli o membrana.</span></a></u></p>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Softwares</strong></span><strong> </strong></u></p>\n	<p>\n		Llic&egrave;ncies disponibles per l&rsquo;an&agrave;lisi qualitatiu i quantitatiu de les imatges en:</p>\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n			Metamorph</li>\n		<li>\n			<u><a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/150629_IMARIS%20web_CAT.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Imaris 8 (Bitplane)-Fitxa t&egrave;cnica</span></a></u></li>\n	</ul>\n	<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong><u>R</u></strong><u><strong>eserves</strong></u></span>\n	<p>\n		Pel que fa a les reserves dels equips del Laboratori de Microsc&ograve;pia de l&rsquo;INc, els membres de l&rsquo;INc tindran prefer&egrave;ncia sobre la resta de personal. La utilitzaci&oacute; dels microscopis podr&agrave; ser en autoservei o amb suport t&egrave;cnic. Les reserves es podran realitzar de 3 maneres diferents: e-mail (<a href=\"mailto:inc.microscopia@uab.cat\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">inc.microscopia@uab.cat</span></a>), tel&egrave;fon (93-5812733) o internet (consultar amb el t&egrave;cnic per donar-se d&rsquo;alta en aquesta modalitat).</p>\n	<p>\n		<u><a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/170113_Normativa%20reserves%20web_CAT.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Normativa de reserves</span></a></u></p>\n	<p>\n		<br />\n		<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Horaris i Tarifes </strong></span></u></p>\n	<p>\n		L&rsquo;horari d&rsquo;obertura del laboratori de Microsc&ograve;pia &eacute;s de 9 a 17h, tot i que els usuaris que funcionin amb autoservei i estiguin autoritzats pel t&egrave;cnic, podran utilitzar-lo fora de l&rsquo;horari establert, en caps de setmana i festius (sempre i quan hagin tramitat correctament l&rsquo;autoritzaci&oacute; pertinent per tenir acc&eacute;s al laboratori de Microsc&ograve;pia durant caps de setmana i vacances, demanar al t&egrave;cnic).</p>\n	<p>\n		L&rsquo;horari de tarificaci&oacute; normal (sense reducci&oacute;) &eacute;s de 9:00 a 19:00h.</p>\n	<p>\n		<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/161123_Proposta%20Tarifes%202017_DEF%20(2)(1).pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Tarifes&nbsp;2017&nbsp;</u></a><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/NOU.gif\" style=\"width: 26px; height: 13px;\" /></strong></u></span></p>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Per a m&eacute;s informaci&oacute; contactar amb:</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<strong>N&uacute;ria Barba Bosch</strong></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	T&egrave;cnic especialista Laboratori de Microsc&ograve;pia INc</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Edifici M, despatx M1/108, laboratori M1-147</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies-Facultat de Medicina</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Tel: 935812733&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Fax: 935812390&nbsp;</div>\n',10,1,0),(704,52,0,'Laboratorios técnicos del INc',NULL,7,0,1),(706,52,0,'Cultivos celulares','<div>\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n		<p>\n			El laboratorio de cultivos celulares del Inc es un laboratorio destinado a facilitar los recursos necesarios para trabajar con l&iacute;neas celulares y cultivos primarios para su posterior evaluaci&oacute;n cualitativa y cuantitativa mediante diferentes t&eacute;cnicas.</p>\n		<p>\n			Para ello, el laboratorio cuenta con personal t&eacute;cnico cualificado y experimentado, as&iacute; como con equipos con diferentes prestaciones.</p>\n		<p>\n			Este laboratorio y equipos est&aacute;n a disposici&oacute;n de los grupos del INc, investigadores de la UAB e instituciones p&uacute;blicas y privadas.</p>\n		<p>\n			&nbsp;</p>\n		<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n			<tbody>\n				<tr>\n					<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n						<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/DSC00244.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n					<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n						<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/gfap_5.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 114px;\" /></td>\n					<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n						<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/DSC00260.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 114px;\" /></td>\n				</tr>\n			</tbody>\n		</table>\n		<p>\n			<br />\n			<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Las tareas que realizan los t&eacute;cnicos del INc son: </strong></span></u></p>\n		<ul>\n			<li>\n				Mantenimiento y coordinaci&oacute;n del uso de equipos comunes del INc de su &nbsp;especialidad.</li>\n			<li>\n				Formaci&oacute;n en t&eacute;cnicas especializadas desarrolladas por el t&eacute;cnico especialista.</li>\n			<li>\n				Formaci&oacute;n obligatoria para usuarios en r&eacute;gimen de autoservicio.</li>\n			<li>\n				Realizaci&oacute;n de procedimientos experimentales por parte del t&eacute;cnico especialista.</li>\n		</ul>\n	</div>\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n		<u><a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(580,1);\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">T&eacute;cnicas ofertadas</span></a></u></div>\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n		&nbsp;</div>\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n		<p>\n			<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Equipamiento</strong></span></u></p>\n		<p>\n			Actualmente el laboratorio cuenta con tres salas de cultivos celulares, una destinada al trabajo con l&iacute;neas celulares, otra para cultivos primarios y una tercera de uso para cualquier procedimiento de los anteriores. Adem&aacute;s, estos laboratorios cuentan con equipos que tambi&eacute;n est&aacute;n a disposici&oacute;n del Inc, que aun no estando en las salas, son necesarios para llevar a cabo el trabajo en cultivos.</p>\n		<ul>\n			<li>\n				<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Castellano/index.php#!/M2-103-%20Lineas%20celulares_573_1\" target=\"_blank\"><u><span style=\"color:#000000;\">M2/103. Sala de l&iacute;neas celulares</span></u></a></li>\n			<li>\n				<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Castellano/index.php#!/M2-104-%20L%C3%ADneas%20celulares%20y%20cultivos%20primarios_571_1\" target=\"_blank\"><u><span style=\"color:#000000;\">M2/104. Sala mixta</span></u></a></li>\n			<li>\n				<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Castellano/index.php#!/M2-130.2-%20Cultivos%20primarios_572_1\" target=\"_blank\"><u><span style=\"color:#000000;\">M2/130.2. Sala de cultivos primarios</span></u></a></li>\n			<li>\n				<u><a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/equipamiento%20gral%20todas%20salas%20cast.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Equipos generales en todas las salas</span></a></u></li>\n			<li>\n				<u><a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(574,1);\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Equipos asociados&nbsp; a cultivos</span></a></u></li>\n		</ul>\n	</div>\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n		<p>\n			&nbsp;</p>\n		<p>\n			<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Condiciones generales</strong></span></u></p>\n		Los miembros del Inc tendr&aacute;n preferencia sobre los no miembros y dentro de estos, los que no hayan utilizado anteriormente los laboratorios o equipos comunes tendr&aacute;n preferencia respecto a los que lo hayan hecho recientemente. Otro par&aacute;metro importante ser&aacute; el orden de recepci&oacute;n de peticiones y la posibilidad del t&eacute;cnico de intercalarlas con otras solicitudes.\n		<p>\n			&nbsp;</p>\n		<p>\n			<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Tarifas&nbsp; </strong></span></u></p>\n		<p>\n			<u><a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/161123_Proposta%20Tarifes%202017_DEF%20(2)(1).pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Tarifas</a><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/161123_Proposta%20Tarifes%202017_DEF%20(2)(1).pdf\" target=\"_blank\">&nbsp;2017&nbsp;</a></u><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/NOU.gif\" style=\"width: 26px; height: 13px;\" /></strong></u></span></p>\n		<div>\n			&nbsp;</div>\n		<p>\n			&nbsp;</p>\n		<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n			<tbody>\n				<tr>\n					<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n						<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Ra0_25dbx20xmerge.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 111px;\" /></td>\n					<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n						<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/DSC00238.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 111px;\" /></td>\n					<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n						<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/DSC00254.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 111px;\" /></td>\n				</tr>\n			</tbody>\n		</table>\n		<p>\n			&nbsp;</p>\n		<p>\n			Para m&aacute;s informaci&oacute;n y pedidos dir&iacute;janse a:</p>\n	</div>\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n		&nbsp;</div>\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n		<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Castellano/profile.php?id=77\"><strong>Cristina Guti&eacute;rrez Salvador</strong></a><br />\n		Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</div>\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n		Unitat de Bioqu&iacute;mica i Biolog&iacute;a Molecular</div>\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n		Facultat de Medicina</div>\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n		<a href=\"mailto:inc.cultius@uab.es\">inc.cultius@uab.es&nbsp;</a></div>\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n		Tel: 935814828</div>\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n		Fax: 935811573</div>\n</div>\n',8,1,1),(707,52,0,'Histología','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	El Laboratorio de Histolog&iacute;a del INc es un laboratorio destinado a facilitar el procesamiento de diferentes tipos de muestras para su posterior evaluaci&oacute;n cualitativa y cuantitativa mediante microscop&iacute;a &oacute;ptica y/o confocal.<br />\n	Para ello el laboratorio cuenta con personal t&eacute;cnico cualificado y experimentado, as&iacute; como con equipos con muchas prestaciones (ver listado m&aacute;s abajo).<br />\n	Este laboratorio y equipos est&aacute;n a disposici&oacute;n de los grupos del INc, investigadores de la UAB e instituciones p&uacute;blicas y privadas.</p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n				<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/Criotomia_medul_la_ratoli.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n			<td>\n				<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/hist2.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<br />\n	<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Las tareas que realizan los t&eacute;cnicos del INc son:</strong></span></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n		Mantenimiento y coordinaci&oacute;n del uso de aparatos comunes del INc de su especialidad.</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n		Formaci&oacute;n en t&eacute;cnicas especializadas desarrolladas por el t&eacute;cnico especialista.</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n		Formaci&oacute;n obligatoria para usuarios en r&eacute;gimen de autoservicio.</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n		Realizaci&oacute;n de procedimientos experimentales por parte del t&eacute;cnico especialista.</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<u><strong><span style=\"color:#800000;\">T&eacute;cnicas ofrecidas</span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<div>\n			Procesamiento histol&oacute;gico de inclusi&oacute;n en parafina (solo por parte del t&eacute;cnico especialista)</div>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n<div>\n	<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/TarifasparafinaAll.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> -</span></a></strong><u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/TarifasparafinaAll.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Tarifas material de inclusi&oacute;n</span></a><br />\n	</u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/CastTISSUE%20PROCESSOR.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">-</span></a><u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/CastTISSUE%20PROCESSOR.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Tissue processor</span></a><br />\n	</u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/CastPARAFFIN%20EMBEDDING%20STATION.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> -</span></a><u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/CastPARAFFIN%20EMBEDDING%20STATION.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Paraffin embeding station</span></a></u></div>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<div>\n			Procesamiento histol&oacute;gico para congelaci&oacute;n</div>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n		<div>\n			Microtom&iacute;a: <u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/CastLEICA%20MICROTOME%20RM%202255.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">LEICA MICROTOME RM 2255</span></a></u></div>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n		<div>\n			Criotom&iacute;a :<u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/CastSME%20CRYOTOME%20THERMO.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">SME CRYOTOME THERMO</span></a></u>&nbsp; Y <u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/CastCRYOSTAT%20LEICA%20CM3050%20S.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">CRYOSTAT LEICA CM3050S</span></a></u></div>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n		<div>\n			Secciones con vibratomo: <u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/CastLEICA%20VT%201000S.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">LEICA VT 1000S</span></a></u></div>\n	</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n		<div>\n			Coloraciones (Hematoxilina-eosina, azul de touluidina, violeta de cresilo, Hoechst), t&eacute;cnicas histoqu&iacute;micas e inmunohistoqu&iacute;micas / inmunofluorescencia: <u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/CastDAKO%20AUTOSTAINER.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">DAKO AUTOSTAINER</span></a></u>&nbsp; y <u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/GENERAL%20LAB%20EQUIPMENT%20CASTELLANO.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">GENERAL LAB EQUIPMENT</span></a></u></div>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n		<div>\n			Soporte en an&aacute;lisis multiplex: <u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/CastMAGPIX.pdf\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">MAGPIX</span></a></u></div>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Condiciones generales</strong></span></u></p>\n<p>\n	Los miembros del Inc tendr&aacute;n preferencia sobre los no miembros y dentro de estos, los que no hayan utilizado anteriormente los laboratorios o equipos comunes tendr&aacute;n preferencia respecto a los que lo hayan hecho recientemente. Otro par&aacute;metro importante ser&aacute; el orden de recepci&oacute;n de peticiones y la posibilidad del t&eacute;cnico de intercalarlas con otras solicitudes.</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Tarifas&nbsp; </strong></span></u></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/161123_Proposta%20Tarifes%202017_DEF%20(2)(1).pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Tarifas&nbsp;2017&nbsp;</u></a><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/NOU.gif\" style=\"width: 26px; height: 13px;\" /></strong></u></span></p>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<span style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</span><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/hist1.JPG\" style=\"width: 25%;\" /><span style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Para m&aacute;s informaci&oacute;n y/o pedidos dir&iacute;janse a:<br />\n	<br />\n	<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Castellano/profile.php?id=40\"><strong>Mar Castillo Ruiz</strong></a><br />\n	Lab M1/109-M1/110. Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies<br />\n	Torre M-1ra planta<a href=\"mailto:inc.histologia@uab.cat\"><br />\n	<strong><em><span style=\"color:#000000;\">inc.histologia@uab.cat</span></em></strong></a><br />\n	Tel: 935862733<br />\n	Fax:935814152</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n',9,1,1),(708,52,0,'Microscopía','<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<p>\n		El Laboratorio de Microscop&iacute;a del INc es un laboratorio destinado a facilitar la observaci&oacute;n de diferentes tipos de muestras, para poder evaluarlas cualitativa y cuantitativamente.</p>\n	<p>\n		Este laboratorio, localizado en la M1-147 de la Facultad de Medicina de la UAB, est&aacute; a disposici&oacute;n de los grupos del INc, investigadores de la UAB e instituciones p&uacute;blicas y privadas.</p>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Tareas que realiza el t&eacute;cnico del Laboratorio de Microscop&iacute;a </strong></span></u></p>\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n			Mantenimiento y coordinaci&oacute;n del uso de los diferentes microscopios propios del Laboratorio de Microscop&iacute;a.</li>\n		<li>\n			Soporte t&eacute;cnico en el uso de los microscopios y softwares de procesamiento de imagen (ImageJ, Metamorph) para personal no formado, ya sea con los propios equipos del INc o en equipos fuera de este, propios de la UAB.</li>\n		<li>\n			Formaci&oacute;n obligatoria para usuarios en r&eacute;gimen de autoservicio.</li>\n		<li>\n			Realizaci&oacute;n de procedimientos experimentales por parte del t&eacute;cnico especialista.</li>\n	</ul>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		<u><strong><span style=\"color:#800000;\">Equipos</span></strong></u></p>\n	<p>\n		Permiten hacer estudios de imagen 3D, fluorescencia m&uacute;ltiple y an&aacute;lisis de colocalizaci&oacute;n, captaci&oacute;n de imagen <em>in vivo</em>, estudios de calcio intracelular, de pH, de potencial de membrana, entre otros.</p>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n		<tbody>\n			<tr>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<u><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/Amaia.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></u></td>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<u><img alt=\"\" height=\"131\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/8DIV_NGCP_G-MAP_R-GFAP_20x_01_3D.jpg\" width=\"195\" /></u></td>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<u><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/Carlos-Barcia_2.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></u></td>\n			</tr>\n		</tbody>\n	</table>\n	<p>\n		<u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/150309_Fitxa%20Zeiss%20LSM700_SP.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Microscopio de rastreo l&aacute;ser confocal (Zeiss LSM 700): M1-147</span></a></u><a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(657,1);\"><br />\n		<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></a></p>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n		<tbody>\n			<tr>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/cerebel_40x_01.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" height=\"120\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/Objs-Eclipse-90i.jpg\" width=\"159\" /></td>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/150205_Marian-Baltrons-90i.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n			</tr>\n		</tbody>\n	</table>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<u><a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(657,1);\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Microscopios &oacute;pticos de epifluorescencia Nikon Eclipse 90i y 80i: M1-147</span></a></u></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(659,1);\"><br />\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></a></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n		<tbody>\n			<tr>\n				<td style=\"width: 50%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/Roser_01.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n				<td>\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/Roser_03.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n			</tr>\n		</tbody>\n	</table>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<u><a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(659,1);\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Microscopios &oacute;pticos de epifluorescencia Nikon Eclipse TE2000-E y TE2000-U: M2-129.1</span></a></u></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Marcadores</strong></span></u></p>\n	<p>\n		Disponemos de una amplia gama de marcadores: <u><a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/150309_llistat%20abs%20i%20marcadors%20web_SP.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">anticuerpos secundarios, estreptavidinas y marcadores directos de n&uacute;cleo o membrana.</span></a></u></p>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		<u><strong style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\">Softwares</strong></u></p>\n	<p>\n		Licencias disponibles para el an&aacute;lisis cualitativo y cuantitativo de las im&aacute;genes en:</p>\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n			Metamorph</li>\n		<li>\n			<u><a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/150629_IMARIS%20web_SP.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Imaris 8 (Bitplane)Ficha tecnica</span></a></u></li>\n	</ul>\n	<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Reservas</strong></span></u>\n	<p>\n		Respecto a las reservas de los equipos del Laboratorio de Microscop&iacute;a del INc, los miembros del INc tendr&aacute;n preferencia sobre el resto de personal. La utilizaci&oacute;n de los microscopios podr&aacute; ser en autoservicio o con soporte t&eacute;cnico. Las reservas se podr&aacute;n realizar de 3 maneras diferentes: e-mail (<a href=\"mailto:inc.microscopia@uab.cat\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">inc.microscopia@uab.cat</span></a>), tel&eacute;fono (93-5812733) o internet (consultar con el t&eacute;cnico para darse de alta en esta modalidad).</p>\n	<p>\n		<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/170113_Normativa%20reserves%20web_SP.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><u><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Normativa de reservas</span></u></a><br />\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Horarios y Tarifas (por hora de uso)</strong></span></u></p>\n	<p>\n		El horario de apertura del Laboratorio de Microscop&iacute;a del INc es de 9 a 17h, aunque los usuarios que trabajen en autoservicio y est&eacute;n autorizados por el t&eacute;cnico, podr&aacute;n utilizarlo a partir de las 17h y los fines de semana (siempre y cuando tengan tramitada correctamente la autorizaci&oacute;n pertinente para tener acceso al laboratorio de Microscop&iacute;a durante fines de semana y vacaciones, pedir al t&eacute;cnico).</p>\n	<p>\n		El horario de tarificaci&oacute;n normal (sin reducci&oacute;n) es de 9:00 a 19:00h.</p>\n	<p>\n		<u><a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/161123_Proposta%20Tarifes%202017_DEF%20(2)(1).pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Tarifas&nbsp;2017&nbsp;</a></u><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/NOU.gif\" style=\"width: 26px; height: 13px;\" /></strong></u></span></p>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<p>\n		Para m&aacute;s informaci&oacute;n&nbsp;contactar con<strong>:</strong></p>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<strong>N&uacute;ria Barba Bosch</strong></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	T&eacute;cnico especialista Laboratorio de Microscop&iacute;a INc</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Edificio M, despacho M1/108, laboratorio M1-147</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies-Facultad de Medicina</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Tel: 935812733&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Fax: 935812390</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n',10,1,1),(709,45,0,'INc technical laboratories',NULL,7,0,2),(711,45,0,'Cell Culture','<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<p>\n		The Inc&rsquo;s Cell Culture Unit is a laboratory designed to provide the necessary resources to work with cell lines and primary cultures for further qualitative and quantitative assessment using different techniques.</p>\n	<p>\n		For this, thelaboratory has qualified and experienced technical staff and equipment with large range of features.<br />\n		<br />\n		This laboratory and equipment are available to INc groups, UAB researchers and public and private entities.</p>\n	<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n		<tbody>\n			<tr>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/DSC00244.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/gfap_5.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 114px;\" /></td>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/DSC00260.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 114px;\" /></td>\n			</tr>\n		</tbody>\n	</table>\n	<p>\n		<br />\n		<span style=\"color:#800000;\"><u><strong>Tasks performed by the Cell Culture Lab technician:</strong></u></span></p>\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n			Maintenance and coordination of the use of INc&rsquo;s common equipment from their field of expertise.</li>\n		<li>\n			Training in specific techniques developed by the specialist technician.</li>\n		<li>\n			Mandatory training for users in self-service regime.</li>\n		<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n			Execution of experimental procedures by the specialist technician<u>.</u></li>\n	</ul>\n	<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n		<u><a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(581,1);\">More info related to techniques offered</a></u></p>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"color:#800000;\"><u><strong>Equipment</strong></u></span></p>\n	<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n		The lab currently has three cell culture rooms, one for working with cell lines, other one to work with primary cultures and a third to use for any of the above procedure. These laboratories have equipment that is also available to Inc, which although not being in the cell culture rooms, is required to carry out the work in cell cultures.</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\n		<u><a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(573,1);\"><br />\n		</a><a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(576,1);\">M2/103. Cell line room</a></u></p>\n	<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\n		<u><a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(577,1);\">M2/104. Mixed room</a></u></p>\n	<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\n		<u><a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(578,1);\">M2/130.2. Primary cell culture room</a></u></p>\n	<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\n		<u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/General%20equipment%20in%20all%20rooms.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">General equipment in all rooms</a></u></p>\n	<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\n		<u><a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(575,1);\">Associated equipment to cell culture rooms</a></u></p>\n</div>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"color:#800000;\"><u><strong>Terms</strong></u></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	INc members have preference over non-members and within these groups, those which have not previously used the equipment will have preference over those who have used it recently. Another important factor is a first arrive first serve basis, and the possibility of the technician to carry on different projects at a time.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<br />\n	<span style=\"color:#800000;\"><u><strong>Pricing quotes</strong></u></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/161123_Proposta%20Tarifes%202017_DEF%20(2)(1).pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Pricing quotes for 2017&nbsp;</u></a><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><u><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/NOU.gif\" style=\"width: 26px; height: 13px;\" /></strong></u></span></p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n				<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Ra0_25dbx20xmerge.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 111px;\" /></td>\n			<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n				<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/DSC00238.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 111px;\" /></td>\n			<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n				<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/DSC00254.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 111px;\" /></td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	For more information and orders please contact:<br />\n	<br />\n	<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/English/profile.php?id=77\"><strong> Cristina Guti&eacute;rrez Salvador</strong></a><br />\n	Institut de&nbsp; Neuroci&egrave;ncies<br />\n	Unitat de Bioqu&iacute;mica i Biolog&iacute;a Molecular<br />\n	Facultat de Medicina<br />\n	<a href=\"mailto:inc.cultius@uab.es\">inc.cultius@uab.es</a><br />\n	Tel: 935814828<br />\n	Fax: 935811573</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n',8,1,2),(712,45,0,'Histology','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	The INc&rsquo;s Histology Unit performs processing of different kind of tissue samples in order to qualitative and quantitative evaluate them through optical and/or confocal microscope techniques.<br />\n	To this end, the lab has qualified and experienced technical staff and equipment with a large range of features (see the list below)<br />\n	The Unit is available to INc groups, UAB researchers and public and private entities.</p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n				<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/Criotomia_medul_la_ratoli.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n			<td>\n				<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/hist2.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n	<br />\n	<u><strong><span style=\"color:#800000;\">Tasks performed by the Histology Lab technician:</span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		Maintenance and coordination of the use of INc&rsquo;s common equipment from their field of expertise.</li>\n	<li>\n		Training in specific techniques developed by the specialist technician.</li>\n	<li>\n		Mandatory training for users in self-service regime.</li>\n	<li>\n		Execution of experimental procedures by the specialist technician.</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Techniques offered</strong></span></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		Histological processing for paraffin embedding (only by technician)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> -</span><u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/TarifasparafinaAll.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Paraffin embedding material rates</span></a><br />\n	<br />\n	</u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp; </span><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/EngTISSUE%20PROCESSOR.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">-</span></a><u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/EngTISSUE%20PROCESSOR.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Tissue Processor</span></a><br />\n	<br />\n	</u><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/EngPARAFFIN%20EMBEDDING%20STATION.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">-</span></a><u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/EngPARAFFIN%20EMBEDDING%20STATION.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Parafine embedding station</span></a></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		Histological processing for freezing<br />\n		&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>\n		Microtomy: <u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/EngLEICA%20MICROTOME%20RM%202255.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">LEICA MICROTOME RM 2255 </span></a></u><br />\n		&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>\n		Cryotomy: <u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/EngSME%20CRYOTOME%20THERMO.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">SME CRYOTOME THERMO</span></a></u>&nbsp; and <u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/EngCRYOSTAT%20LEICA%20CM3050%20S.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">CRYOSTAT LEICA CM3050S </span></a></u><br />\n		&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>\n		Vibratome sectioning: <u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/ENgLEICA%20VT%201000S.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">LEICA VT 1000S </span></a></u><br />\n		&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>\n		Stains (Hematoxylin-eosin, toluidine blue, cresyl violet, Hoechst), histochemistry and immunohistochemistry/immunofluorescence: <u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/EngDAKO%20AUTOSTAINER.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">DAKO AUTOSTAINER</span></a><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;</span></u>and <u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/GENERAL%20LAB%20EQUIPMENT%20ENGLISH.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">GENERAL LAB EQUIPMENT </span></a></u><br />\n		&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>\n		Support in multiplex analysis: <u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/EngMAGPIX.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">MAGPIX </span></a></u></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"color:#800000;\"><u><strong>Terms</strong></u></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	INc members have preference over non-members and within these groups, those which have not previously used the equipment will have preference over those who have used it recently. Another important factor is a first arrive first serve basis, and the possibility of the technician to carry on different projects at a time.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<br />\n	<br />\n	<span style=\"color:#800000;\"><u><strong>Pricing quotes</strong></u></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/161123_Proposta%20Tarifes%202017_DEF%20(2)(1).pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Pricing quotes for 2017&nbsp;</a></u><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/NOU.gif\" style=\"width: 26px; height: 13px;\" /></strong></u></span></p>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<span style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</span><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/hist1.JPG\" style=\"width: 25%;\" /><span style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	For more information and orders please contact:<br />\n	<br />\n	<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/English/profile.php?id=40\"><strong>Mar Castillo Ruiz</strong></a><br />\n	Lab M1/109-M1/110. Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies<br />\n	Torre M-1st floor<a href=\"mailto:inc.histologia@uab.cat\"><br />\n	inc.histologia@uab.cat</a><br />\n	Tel: 935862733<br />\n	Fax: 935814152</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n',9,1,2),(713,45,0,'Microscope Unit','<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<p>\n		The INc Microscope Unit facilitates experimental design, training and procedures in microscope imaging studies of different biological and research samples. It is located at room M1-147 at INc, Faculty of Medicine of the UAB and is available for INc groups, for UAB researchers and public and private institutions.</p>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Tasks performed by the Microscope Unit technicians </strong></span></u></p>\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n			Maintenance and coordination of the usage of different microscopes from the microscopy lab.</li>\n		<li>\n			Technical support in working with microscopes and imaging processing softwares (ImageJ and Metamorph) for untrained users. This support is offered for INc&rsquo;s equipment as well as for other external equipment, owned by UAB.</li>\n		<li>\n			Obligatory training for auto-service users.</li>\n		<li>\n			Realization of experimental procedures by specialist technician.</li>\n	</ul>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Equipment</strong></span></u></p>\n	<p>\n		Allows research studies in 3D image, multiple fluorescence and colocalization, <em>in vivo </em>imaging, studies of cellular intracellular calcium, pH, membrane potential, and others.</p>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n		<tbody>\n			<tr>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/Amaia.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" height=\"131\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/8DIV_NGCP_G-MAP_R-GFAP_20x_01_3D.jpg\" width=\"195\" /></td>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/Carlos-Barcia_2.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n			</tr>\n		</tbody>\n	</table>\n	<p style=\"text-align: left;\">\n		<u><u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/150309_Fitxa%20Zeiss%20LSM700_EN.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Confocal laser scanning microscope (Zeiss LSM 700): M1-147</a></u></u></p>\n	<p style=\"text-align: left;\">\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n		<tbody>\n			<tr>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/cerebel_40x_01.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" height=\"120\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/Objs-Eclipse-90i.jpg\" width=\"159\" /></td>\n				<td style=\"width: 33%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/150205_Marian-Baltrons-90i.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n			</tr>\n		</tbody>\n	</table>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<u><a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(658,1);\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Optical epifluorescence microscopes Nikon Eclipse 90i and 80i: M1-147</span></a></u></div>\n<div>\n	<strong><u><a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(656,1);\"><br />\n	</a></u></strong></div>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n		<tbody>\n			<tr>\n				<td style=\"width: 50%;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/Roser_01.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n				<td>\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/Roser_03.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></td>\n			</tr>\n		</tbody>\n	</table>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<u><a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(660,1);\">Optical epifluorescence microscopes Nikon Eclipse TE2000-E i TE2000-U: M2-129.1</a></u></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Markers</strong></span></u></p>\n	<p>\n		A wide range of different markers is also available<strong><em>:<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></em></strong><u><a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/150309_llistat%20abs%20i%20marcadors%20web_EN.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">secondary antibodies, streptavidin and nuclear or membrane direct markers.</span></a></u></p>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Softwares</strong></span></u></p>\n	<p>\n		Available licenses for qualitative or quantitative image analysis:</p>\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n			&nbsp;Metamorph</li>\n		<li>\n			<u>I<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/150629_IMARIS%20web_EN.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">maris 8 (Bitplane) Technical sheet </span></a></u></li>\n	</ul>\n	<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Terms</strong></span></u></p>\n	<p>\n		INc members have priority over the rest of users. Use of microscope could be self-service or under direct guidance of a technician. Booking of microscopes could be done in 3 different ways: e-mail (<a href=\"mailto:inc.microscopia@uab.cat\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">inc.microscopia@uab.cat</span></a>), phone (93-5812733) or internet (requires contacting the technician to register in this way).</p>\n	<p>\n		<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/170113_Normativa%20reserves%20web_EN.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><u><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Rules of booking</span></u></a></p>\n	<p>\n		<br />\n		<u><span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Schedule and rates (per hour of usage)</strong></span></u></p>\n	<p>\n		The daily INc Microscope Unit schedule is from 9:00 am to 5:00 pm, although users, who work in self-service mode with prior technician authorization, can use it from 5:00 pm on and at the weekends/holidays. In this latter case, users need to process the authorization for accessing the Microscope Unit during weekends and holidays. Prior building access authorization is required, and can request to the technician.</p>\n	<p>\n		Regular pricing quotes are from 9:00 am to 7:00 pm.</p>\n	<p>\n		<u><a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/161123_Proposta%20Tarifes%202017_DEF%20(2)(1).pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Pricing quotes for 2017&nbsp;</a></u><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/NOU.gif\" style=\"width: 26px; height: 13px;\" /></strong></u></span></p>\n	<div>\n		&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<br />\n	For more information please contact:<br />\n	<br />\n	<strong>N&uacute;ria Barba Bosch</strong><br />\n	Specialist Technician of INc Microscope Unit<br />\n	M Building, Office M1/108<br />\n	Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies-Faculty of Medicine<br />\n	Phone: 935812733<br />\n	Fax: 935812390</p>\n',10,1,2),(715,52,0,'Premios y Méritos',NULL,14,0,1),(716,52,0,'ICREA Academia','<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n				<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>2014</strong></span></td>\n			<td>\n				&nbsp;</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n				<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\">ICREA ACADEMIA, Roser Nadal</span></span></strong></td>\n			<td>\n				&nbsp;</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n				<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Castellano/profile.php?id=104\">Roser Nadal Alemany</a> es profesora del&nbsp;Departamento de Psicobiologia y de Metodolog&iacute;a de las Ciencias de la Salud&nbsp;y miembro del <em>Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</em>. Su investigaci&oacute;n trata sobre los mecanismos por los que el estr&eacute;s incrementa la vulnerabilidad en la psicopatologia, como la ansiedad, la adicci&oacute;n, el estr&eacute;s post-traum&aacute;tico, la depresi&oacute;n o la impulsividad, utilizando modelos animales. La Dra. Nadal est&aacute; especialmente interesada en las diferencias individuales en la reactividad al estr&eacute;s y los factores involucrados en la resistencia a los efectos negativos del mismo.</td>\n			<td>\n				<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n					<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/RNadalICREA.JPG\" style=\"width: 95px; margin: 10px; height: 106px;\" /></strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n				<br />\n				<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>2013</strong></span></td>\n			<td>\n				&nbsp;</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n				<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\">ICREA ACADEMIA, Alberto Fern&aacute;ndez-Teruel</span></span></strong></td>\n			<td>\n				&nbsp;</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n				<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Castellano/profile.php?id=63\">Alberto Fernandez-Teruel</a> es profesor del Departamento de Psiquiatr&iacute;a y Medicina Legal y miembro del <em>Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</em>. Las investigaciones del Dr. Fernandez-Teruel tienen como objetivo mejorar el conocimiento sobre las bases psicol&oacute;gicas, neurobiol&oacute;gicos y gen&eacute;ticas de varias enfermedades psicol&oacute;gicas y neurol&oacute;gicas como son los procesos relacionados con el estr&eacute;s, la impulsividad, la adicci&oacute;n, esquizofrenia o envejecimiento.</td>\n			<td>\n				<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/AFerndef.jpg\" style=\"width: 95px; height: 116px; margin: 10px;\" /></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n				<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>2011</strong></span></td>\n			<td>\n				&nbsp;</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n				<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\">ICREA ACADEMIA, Carlos A Saura</span></span></strong></td>\n			<td>\n				&nbsp;</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n				<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Castellano/profile.php?id=126\">Carlos A. Saura</a> es profesor del Departamento de Bioqu&iacute;mica y Biolog&iacute;a Molecular (Facultad de Medicina) y miembro del <em>Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</em>, donde lidera el grupo de Neurobiolog&iacute;a de la enfermedad de Alzheimer. Su investigaci&oacute;n est&aacute; dirigida a dilucidar los mecanismos de disfunci&oacute;n neuronal y sin&aacute;ptica en la enfermedad de Alzheimer, as&iacute; como a dise&ntilde;ar nuevas estrategias terap&eacute;uticas para prevenir y/o revertir la disfunci&oacute;n cognitiva en esta enfermedad.</td>\n			<td>\n				<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/ICREACSaura.jpg\" style=\"width: 95px; height: 63px; margin: 10px;\" /></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<span style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"display: none;\"> </span><br />\n	<span style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n',15,1,1),(718,45,0,'Seminars 2014','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<strong>JANUARY 21ST</strong><br />\n	<span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Whole genome association in outbred rats</strong></span><br />\n	<strong>JONATHAN FLINT</strong><br />\n	Wellcome Trust Centre for Human Genetics, University of Oxford</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<strong>FEBRUARY 14TH </strong><br />\n	<span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Funciones de Semaforinas y Plexinas en la migraci&oacute;n de neuronas pioneras en la corteza en desarrollo</strong></span><br />\n	<strong>JOS&