" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Entrevista completa <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Castellano/#!/_535_1\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Disfrutad!</p>\n','INcentivemos el conocimiento: Bioinformática y neurofarmacología molecular','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-09-09','',0,NULL,1),(127,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	After vacation, again with an interesting aspect of the research related to neuroscience: bioinform&agrave;tics and molecular neuropharmacology. New INcitate Knowledge&rsquo;s interview with James Dalton.</p>\n<p>\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/DSC00323.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></p>\n<p>\n	Full interview <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/English/#!/_536_1\">here</a></p>\n<p>\n	Enjoy!</p>\n','INcite Knowledge: Bioinformatics and molecular neuropharmacology','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-09-09','',0,NULL,2),(128,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	El proper&nbsp; 29 d&rsquo;octubre es celebrar&agrave; la primera trobada del&nbsp; CORE de Salut Mental&nbsp; de la UAB: Vulnerabilitat, Resili&egrave;ncia i Biomarcadors en Psicopatologia (<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/CORE%20Seminar_vcatala_final1.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">programa</a>), a l&rsquo;auditori del nou Hospital de Sant Pau. La Jornada, a m&eacute;s de tenir presentacions i taula rodona, comptar&agrave; amb sessi&oacute; de p&ograve;sters.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/core-salut/\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"86\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/CORElogoSalutMental.jpg\" width=\"154\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	El comit&egrave; cient&iacute;fic organitzador, est&agrave; format, entre d&#39;altres, per la Dra. Roser Nadal, el Dr. Adolf Tobe&ntilde;a i el Dr. Antonio Armario,&nbsp; de l&rsquo;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	M&eacute;s informaci&oacute; de l&#39;esdeveniment ,<a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/investigar/primer-core-seminar-en-salut-mental/presentacio-1345675358908.html\" target=\"_blank\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n','Primer seminari del CORE de Salut mental de la UAB','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-09-23','',0,NULL,0),(129,NULL,'<p>\n	El pr&oacute;ximo 29 de octubre se celebra el primer encuentro del &ldquo;CORE de Salut Mental de la UAB&rdquo;:&nbsp; &nbsp;Vulnerabilidad, resiliencia, y Biomarcadores en Psicopatolog&iacute;a (<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/CORE%20Seminar_vcatala_final1.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">programa</a>), en el auditorio del nuevo Hospital de Sant Pau. La Jornada, adem&aacute;s de tener presentaciones y mesa redonda, contar&aacute; con sesi&oacute;n de posters.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/core-salut/\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"86\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/CORElogoSalutMental.jpg\" width=\"154\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	El comit&eacute; cient&iacute;fico organizador, est&aacute; formado, entre otros,&nbsp; por la Dra. Roser Nadal, el Dr. Adolf Tobe&ntilde;a y el Dr. Antonio Armario, del &ldquo;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies&rdquo;.</p>\n<p>\n	M&aacute;s informaci&oacute;n del evento, <a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/investigar/primer-core-seminar-en-salut-mental/presentacio-1345675358908.html\" target=\"_blank\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n','Primer seminario del \"CORE de Salut Mental de la UAB\"','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-09-23','',0,NULL,1),(130,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	On 29th October, will be held the first meeting of the &ldquo;CORE de Salut Mental de la UAB&rdquo;: <strong><em>Vulnerability, Resilience and Biomarkers in Psychopathology </em></strong>&nbsp;(<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/CORE%20Seminar_vcatala_final1.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">program</a>),at the new Hospital de Sant Pau&rsquo;s auditorium. The seminar will feature posters session, in addition to presentations and roundtable.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/core-salut/\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"86\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/CORElogoSalutMental.jpg\" width=\"154\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	The scientific organizing committee, is made, among others,&nbsp; by Dr. Roser Nadal, Dr. Adolf Tobe&ntilde;a and Dr. Antonio Armario, members of the &ldquo;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies&middot;&rdquo;</p>\n<p>\n	More event info, <a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/investigar/primer-core-seminar-en-salut-mental/presentacio-1345675358908.html\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></p>\n','First seminar of the \"CORE de Salut mental de la UAB\"','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-09-23','',0,NULL,2),(131,NULL,'<p>\n	&ldquo;Diario M&eacute;dico&rdquo; ha entrevistat a la Dra. Olga Pol, amb motiu de la publicaci&oacute; d&rsquo;un article a la revista <em><a href=\"http://jpet.aspetjournals.org/gca?gca=jpet%3B351%2F1%2F224&amp;allch=&amp;submit=Go\" target=\"_blank\">Journal of Pharmacology and Experimental Therapeutics</a>:</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<br />\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/OPol.JPG\" style=\"width: 45%;\" /></p>\n<p>\n	<a href=\"http://bioquimica-clinica.diariomedico.com/2014/09/22/area-cientifica/especialidades/bioquimica-clinica/enzima-copp-potencia-efectos-analgesicos\" title=\"http://bioquimica-clinica.diariomedico.com/2014/09/22/area-cientifica/especialidades/bioquimica-clinica/enzima-copp-potencia-efectos-analgesicos\nCtrl+feu clic o toqueu per seguir l\'enllaç\">http://bioquimica-clinica.diariomedico.com/2014/09/22/area-cientifica/especialidades/bioquimica-clinica/enzima-copp-potencia-efectos-analgesicos</a></p>\n','Entrevista a la Dra. Olga Pol','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-09-30','',1,NULL,0),(132,NULL,'<p>\n	Diario M&eacute;dico, ha entrevistado a la Dra. Olga Pol, con motivo de la publicaci&oacute;n de un art&iacute;culo en la revista <em><a href=\"http://jpet.aspetjournals.org/gca?gca=jpet%3B351%2F1%2F224&amp;allch=&amp;submit=Go\" target=\"_blank\">Journal of Pharmacology and Experimental Therapeutics</a>:</em></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<br />\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/OPol.JPG\" style=\"width: 45%;\" /></p>\n<p>\n	<a href=\"http://bioquimica-clinica.diariomedico.com/2014/09/22/area-cientifica/especialidades/bioquimica-clinica/enzima-copp-potencia-efectos-analgesicos\" title=\"http://bioquimica-clinica.diariomedico.com/2014/09/22/area-cientifica/especialidades/bioquimica-clinica/enzima-copp-potencia-efectos-analgesicos\nCtrl+feu clic o toqueu per seguir l\'enllaç\">http://bioquimica-clinica.diariomedico.com/2014/09/22/area-cientifica/especialidades/bioquimica-clinica/enzima-copp-potencia-efectos-analgesicos</a></p>\n','Entrevista a la Dra. Olga Pol','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-09-30','',1,NULL,1),(133,NULL,'<p>\n	&ldquo;Diario M&eacute;dico&rdquo; has interviewed Dr. Olga Pol on the occasion of the publication of an article in the <em><a href=\"http://jpet.aspetjournals.org/gca?gca=jpet%3B351%2F1%2F224&amp;allch=&amp;submit=Go\" target=\"_blank\">Journal of Pharmacology and Experimental Therapeutics</a>:</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<br />\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/OPol.JPG\" style=\"width: 45%;\" /></p>\n<p>\n	<a href=\"http://bioquimica-clinica.diariomedico.com/2014/09/22/area-cientifica/especialidades/bioquimica-clinica/enzima-copp-potencia-efectos-analgesicos\" title=\"http://bioquimica-clinica.diariomedico.com/2014/09/22/area-cientifica/especialidades/bioquimica-clinica/enzima-copp-potencia-efectos-analgesicos\nCtrl+feu clic o toqueu per seguir l\'enllaç\">http://bioquimica-clinica.diariomedico.com/2014/09/22/area-cientifica/especialidades/bioquimica-clinica/enzima-copp-potencia-efectos-analgesicos</a></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','Dr Olga Pol\'s inverview','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-09-30','',1,NULL,2),(134,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	El proper divendres, s&rsquo;inaugura de forma oficial, el curs acad&egrave;mic del m&agrave;ster de Neuroci&egrave;ncies. Aprofitant la conferencia programada amb el <a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/ICampbell0310.JPG\" target=\"_blank\">Dr. Iain Campbell</a>, s&rsquo;inaugurar&agrave; tamb&eacute; una petita mostra permanent de <a href=\"http://www.neurojewelry.com/\">Neurojoies</a>, es podran veure creacions art&iacute;stiques realitzades pel Dr.Bernardo Castellano, inspirades en la complexa morfologia de neurones i c&egrave;l&middot;lules glials.</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/neurojoyas.jpg\" style=\"width: 60%;\" /><br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	M&eacute;s informaci&oacute; del&nbsp; seminari a la secci&oacute; d&rsquo;<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Catala/#!/Activitats_532_1\">activitats</a></p>\n','Inauguració exposició permanent Neurojoies amb motiu del seminari del 3 d’octubre','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-09-30','',0,NULL,0),(135,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	El pr&oacute;ximo viernes 3 de octubre, se inaugura de forma oficial el curso acad&eacute;mico del m&aacute;ster de Neurociencias. Aprovechando la conferencia programada con el <a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/ICampbell0310.JPG\" target=\"_blank\">Dr. Iain Campbell</a>, se inaugurar&aacute; una peque&ntilde;a muestra permanente de <a href=\"http://www.neurojewelry.com/\">Neurojoyas</a>, se podr&aacute;n ver &nbsp;creaciones art&iacute;sticas realizadas por el Dr. Bernardo Castellano, inspiradas en la intrincada morfolog&iacute;a de neuronas y c&eacute;lulas gliales.</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/neurojoyas.jpg\" style=\"width: 60%;\" /><br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	M&aacute;s informaci&oacute;n del seminario en la secci&oacute;n de <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Castellano/#!/Actividades_531_1\">actividades</a></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','Inauguración exposición permanente Neurojoyas con motivo del seminario del 3 de octubre','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-09-30','',0,NULL,1),(136,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	On FridayOctober 3<sup>rd</sup>, officially opens the academic year of master of Neurosciences.&nbsp; Taking advantage of the scheduled conference with <a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/ICampbell0310.JPG\" target=\"_blank\">Dr. Iain Campbell</a>, a small permanent exhibition called <a href=\"http://www.neurojewelry.com/\">Neurojewelry</a> will open; artistic creations will be on display performed by Dr. Bernardo Castellano, inspired by the intricate morphology of neurons and glial cells.<br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/neurojoyas.jpg\" style=\"width: 60%;\" /><br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	More information about the seminar at our <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/English/#!/Activities_530_1\">activities</a> section</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','Permanent exhibition Neuro Jewelry opening, on occasion of the seminar on October 3rd','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-09-30','',0,NULL,2),(137,NULL,'<p>\n	In the Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies we have wet for ALS, accepting the challenge of Neuroplasticity and Regeneration group.</p>\n<p>\n	Do you want to watch it?</p>\n<p>\n	<iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"281\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/107593118\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></p>\n<p>\n	<a href=\"http://vimeo.com/107593118\">Ice Bucket INc - UAB</a> from <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/user32712039\">Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</a> on <a href=\"https://vimeo.com\">Vimeo</a>.</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	Thanks Quino and Jessica for the good work.</p>\n','We get wet for ALS!!','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-10-01','',0,NULL,2),(138,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	A l&rsquo;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies ens hem mullat per l&#39; ELA, acceptant el repte del grup de Neuroplasticitat i Regeneraci&oacute;.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Voleu veure&#39;l?</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"281\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/107593118\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></p>\n<p>\n	<a href=\"http://vimeo.com/107593118\">Ice Bucket INc - UAB</a> from <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/user32712039\">Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</a> on <a href=\"https://vimeo.com\">Vimeo</a>.</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	Gr&agrave;cies al Quino i la Jessica per la bona feina.</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','Ens mullem per l\' ELA!','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-10-01','',0,NULL,0),(139,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	En el Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies nos hemos mojado por la ELA, aceptando el reto del grupo de Neuroplasticidad y Regeneraci&oacute;n.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&iquest;Quer&eacute;is verlo?</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"281\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/107593118\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></p>\n<p>\n	<a href=\"http://vimeo.com/107593118\">Ice Bucket INc - UAB</a> from <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/user32712039\">Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</a> on <a href=\"https://vimeo.com\">Vimeo</a>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Gracias a Quino y Jessica por el buen trabajo.</p>\n','Nos mojamos por la ELA!!','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-10-01','',0,NULL,1),(140,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Els propers 22 i 23 d&rsquo;octubre, tindr&agrave; lloc el IX Simposi de Neurobiologia Experimental, on l&rsquo;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies col&middot;labora en l&rsquo;organitzaci&oacute;. El simposi es celebrar&agrave; a la seu de la Societat Catalana de Biologia.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://blogs.iec.cat/scb/\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/SCB.jpg\" style=\"width: 40%;\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Dins d&rsquo;aquestes jornades, podreu trobar treballs i darrers resultats &nbsp;de nombrosos membres de l&rsquo;INc.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/SimposiNeurobiologia.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Programa i llibret</a></p>\n','IX Simposi de Neurobiologia Experimental','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-10-17','',1,NULL,0),(141,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Los pr&oacute;ximos 22 y 23 de octubre, tendr&aacute; lugar el IX Simposio de Neurobiolog&iacute;a Experimental, donde el &ldquo;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies&rdquo; colabora en la organizaci&oacute;n. El simposio se celebrar&aacute; en la sede de la &ldquo;Societat Catalana de Biologia&rdquo;.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://blogs.iec.cat/scb/\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/SCB.jpg\" style=\"width: 40%;\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Dentro de estas jornadas, se podr&aacute;n encontrar trabajos y &uacute;ltimos resultados de numerosos miembros del INc.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/SimposiNeurobiologia.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Programa y libreto</a></p>\n','IX Simposio de Neurobiología Experimental ','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-10-17','',1,NULL,1),(142,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Next 22 and 23 of October, will&nbsp; take place the IX Symposium of Experimental Neurobiology, where &ldquo;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies&rdquo; collaborates in the organization. The symposium will be held in the &ldquo;Societat Catalana de Biologia&rdquo; headquarters.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://blogs.iec.cat/scb/\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/SCB.jpg\" style=\"width: 40%;\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	You will find many works and recent results of several INc members within these symposia.</p>\n<p>\n	<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/SimposiNeurobiologia.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Program and abstract book</a></p>\n','IX Symposium of Experimental Neurobiology','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-10-17','',1,NULL,2),(143,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	La Federation of European Neuroscience Societies (FENS) &nbsp;ha elaborat conjuntament amb la Society for Neuroscience (SFN), un comunicat sobre la recerca amb animals.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/FENS-SfN%20Joint%20NHP%20Statementpage1.JPG\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/FENS-SfN Joint NHP Statementpage1.JPG\" style=\"width: 40%;\" /></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/FENS-SfN%20Joint%20NHP%20Statementpage2.JPG\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/FENS-SfN Joint NHP Statementpage2.JPG\" style=\"width: 40%;\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	Podeu consultar el comunicat online, <a href=\"http://www.fens.org/About-Neuroscience/News/2014/10/FENS-SfN-JOINT-STATEMENT/\" target=\"_blank\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','Comunicat sobre la recerca amb animals','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-10-23','',1,NULL,0),(144,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	La Federation of European Neuroscience Societies (FENS) &nbsp;ha elaborado de manera conjunta con la Society for Neuroscience (SFN), un comunicado sobre la investigaci&oacute;n con animales.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/FENS-SfN%20Joint%20NHP%20Statementpage1.JPG\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/FENS-SfN Joint NHP Statementpage1.JPG\" style=\"width: 40%;\" /></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/FENS-SfN%20Joint%20NHP%20Statementpage2.JPG\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/FENS-SfN Joint NHP Statementpage2.JPG\" style=\"width: 40%;\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	Consultar el comunicado online, <a href=\"http://www.fens.org/About-Neuroscience/News/2014/10/FENS-SfN-JOINT-STATEMENT/\" target=\"_blank\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','Comunicado sobre la investigación con animales','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-10-23','',1,NULL,1),(145,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	The Federation of European Neuroscience Societies (FENS) and the Society for Neuroscience (SFN), have issued a joint statement on animal research.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/FENS-SfN%20Joint%20NHP%20Statementpage1.JPG\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/FENS-SfN Joint NHP Statementpage1.JPG\" style=\"width: 40%;\" /></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/FENS-SfN%20Joint%20NHP%20Statementpage2.JPG\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/FENS-SfN Joint NHP Statementpage2.JPG\" style=\"width: 40%;\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	You can read the statement online, <a href=\"http://www.fens.org/About-Neuroscience/News/2014/10/FENS-SfN-JOINT-STATEMENT/\" target=\"_blank\">here.</a></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','Statement about animal research','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-10-23','',1,NULL,2),(146,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Presentat un nou mapa actualitzat sobre la recerca neurocientifica a Catalunya, on es poden consultar les ubicacions i fitxes dels grups que treballen aquesta disciplina arreu del territori.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Catala/index.php#!/Enlla%C3%A7os-dinter%C3%A8s_235_1\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/mapa_presentacio.jpg\" style=\"width: 50%;\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	L&rsquo;actualitzaci&oacute; de les dades i la coordinaci&oacute; del projecte, ha estat duta a terme per la <a href=\"http://blogs.iec.cat/scb/\" target=\"_blank\">Societat Catalana de Biologia</a>, amb la col&middot;laboraci&oacute; de l&rsquo;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies, entre d&rsquo;altres.</p>\n','Nou mapa de la recerca en Neurociències a Catalunya','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-10-23','',0,NULL,0),(147,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Presentado un nuevo mapa actualizado sobre la investigaci&oacute;n neurocientifica en Catalu&ntilde;a, donde se pueden consultar ubicaciones y fichas de grupos que trabajan esta disciplina a lo largo del territorio.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Castellano/#!/Enlaces-de-inter%C3%A9s_473_1\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/mapa_presentacio.jpg\" style=\"width: 50%;\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	La actualizaci&oacute;n de los datos y la coordinaci&oacute;n del proyecto,&nbsp; ha sido llevada a cabo por la <a href=\"http://blogs.iec.cat/scb/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Societat Catalana de Biologia</em></a>, con la colaboraci&oacute;n del <em>Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</em>, entre otros.</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','Nuevo mapa de la investigación en Neurociencias en Cataluña','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-10-23','',0,NULL,1),(148,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Presented a new updated map on neuroscientific research in Catalonia, where you can see locations and profiles of groups working in this field <span class=\"short_text\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">throughout the</span> <span class=\"hps\">territory.</span></span><br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/English/#!/Links_511_1\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/mapa_presentacio.jpg\" style=\"width: 50%;\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	The updating of data and the coordination of the project, has been carried out by&nbsp; <a href=\"http://blogs.iec.cat/scb/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Societat Catalana de Biologia</em></a>, in collaboration with the <em>Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</em>, among others.</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','New map about Neuroscience research in Catalonia','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-10-23','',0,NULL,2),(149,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Els dies 22 i 23 d&acute;Octubre s&acute;ha celebrat el <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UGCHgnOzwVc\" target=\"_blank\">IX Simposi Neurobiologia Experimental de la Societat Catalana de Biologia</a> (SCB).Un gran nombre d&acute;investigadors de l&acute;INc van presentar els seus resultats en sessions orals i p&ograve;sters. El segon premi al millor p&ograve;ster va ser concedit a l&acute;estudiant de doctorat&nbsp;del Programa de Neuroci&egrave;ncies de l&acute;INc Miriam Javier Torrent.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Durant el Simposi es va anunciar que el proper coordinador de la secci&oacute; de Neurobiologia Experimental de la SCB ser&agrave; l&acute;investigador de l&acute;INc Dr. Carles Saura.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/2n Premi-poster.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:11px;\">El Dr. Carles Saura amb la guanyadora del 2on premi al millor p&ograve;ster Miriam Javier</span></div>\n','IX Simposi de Neurobiologia Experimental- Premis i novetats','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-10-27','',0,NULL,0),(150,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"es\"><span class=\"hps\">Los d&iacute;as</span> <span class=\"hps\">22 y 23</span> <span class=\"hps\">de Octubre</span> <span class=\"hps\">se ha celebrado el</span> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UGCHgnOzwVc\" target=\"_blank\"><em><span class=\"hps\">IX</span> <span class=\"hps\">Simposi</span> <span class=\"hps\">Neurobiologia</span> <span class=\"hps\">Experimental</span></em> <span class=\"hps\">de la <em>Societat Catalana</em></span><em> <span class=\"hps\">de Biologia</span></em> </a><span class=\"hps\">(SCB)</span> <span class=\"hps\">.Un</span> <span class=\"hps\">gran n&uacute;mero</span> <span class=\"hps\">de investigadores</span> <span class=\"hps\">del INc</span> <span class=\"hps\">presentaron sus</span> <span class=\"hps\">resultados</span> <span class=\"hps\">en sesiones</span> <span class=\"hps\">orales</span> <span class=\"hps\">y p&oacute;sters.</span> <span class=\"hps\">El segundo premio</span> <span class=\"hps\">al mejor p&oacute;ster</span> <span class=\"hps\">fue concedido</span> <span class=\"hps\">a la estudiante</span> <span class=\"hps\">de doctorado</span> <span class=\"hps\">del Programa</span> <span class=\"hps\">de Neurociencias</span> <span class=\"hps\">del INc</span> <span class=\"hps\">Miriam</span> <span class=\"hps\">Javier</span> <span class=\"hps\">Torrent.</span><br />\n	<br />\n	<span class=\"hps\">Durante el</span> <span class=\"hps\">simposio</span> <span class=\"hps\">se anunci&oacute; que</span> <span class=\"hps\">el pr&oacute;ximo</span> <span class=\"hps\">coordinador de la secci&oacute;n</span> <span class=\"hps\">de Neurobiolog&iacute;a</span> <span class=\"hps\">Experimental de la</span> <span class=\"hps\">SCB</span> <span class=\"hps\">ser&aacute;</span> <span class=\"hps\">investigador</span> <span class=\"hps\">del<em> Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies&nbsp;</em></span> <span class=\"hps\">Dr.</span> <span class=\"hps\">Carlos</span> <span class=\"hps\">Saura.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/2n Premi-poster.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:11px;\">El Dr. Carles Saura con la ganadora del segundo premio al mejor p&oacute;ster Miriam Javier</span></div>\n','IX Simposi Neurobiologia Experimental- Premios y novedades','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-10-27','',1,NULL,1),(151,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"es\"><span class=\"hps\"><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">On 22 and</span> <span class=\"hps\">23 October</span> <span class=\"hps\">was held</span> <span class=\"hps\">the <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UGCHgnOzwVc\" target=\"_blank\"><em>IX Simposi Neurobiologia Experimental de la Societat Catalana de Biologia </em></a>(SCB)</span><span>. A</span> <span class=\"hps\">large number of researchers</span> <span class=\"hps alt-edited\">presented their results</span> <span class=\"hps\">INc</span> <span class=\"hps\">in oral</span> <span class=\"hps\">and poster</span> <span class=\"hps\">sessions</span><span>.</span> <span class=\"hps\">The second prize</span> <span class=\"hps\">for the best poster</span> <span class=\"hps\">was awarded to</span> our <span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"es\"><span class=\"hps\"><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">Neuroscience</span> <span class=\"hps\">Program </span></span></span></span><span class=\"hps\">PhD student</span> <span class=\"hps\">Miriam</span> <span class=\"hps\">Javier</span> <span class=\"hps\">Torrent.</span><br />\n	<br />\n	<span class=\"hps alt-edited\">During the symposium</span> <span class=\"hps alt-edited\">it was announced</span> <span class=\"hps\">that the next</span> <span class=\"hps\">coordinator</span> of <span class=\"hps\">Experimental</span> <span class=\"hps\">Neurobiology</span> <span class=\"hps\">Section</span> <span class=\"hps\">of SCB</span> <span class=\"hps\">will be </span><span class=\"hps\">Dr.</span> <span class=\"hps\">Carlos</span> <span class=\"hps\">Saura <span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"es\"><span class=\"hps\"><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">researcher at the <em>Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</em>.</span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/2n Premi-poster.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:11px;\">Dr. Carles Saura with <span style=\"font-size:11px;\">Miriam Javier, awarded with the second prize for the best poster</span></span></div>\n','IX Simposi de Neurobiologia Experimental- Awards and news','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-10-27','',0,NULL,2),(152,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	En aquesta ocasi&oacute;, l&rsquo;Esther Udina ens parla de circuits espinals i de la potencialitat de la rehabilitaci&oacute; en pacients neurol&ograve;gics, entre d&rsquo;altres temes.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/DSC00446.JPG\" style=\"width: 60%;\" /></p>\n<p>\n	Gr&agrave;cies pel teu temps Esther!!!</p>\n<p>\n	Veure entrevista completa, <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Catala/#!/_534_1\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n','INcentivem el coneixement- Esther Udina','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-10-28','',0,NULL,0),(153,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	En esta ocasi&oacute;n, Esther Udina nos habla de circuitos espinales y de la potencialidad de la rehabilitaci&oacute;n en pacientes neurol&oacute;gicos, entre otros temas.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/DSC00446.JPG\" style=\"width: 60%;\" /></p>\n<p>\n	Gracias por tu tiempo Esther!!!</p>\n<p>\n	Ver entrevista completa, <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Castellano/#!/_535_1\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n','INcentivemos el conocimiento- Esther Udina','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-10-28','',0,NULL,1),(154,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	This time, Esther Udina talks about spinal circuits and the potential of rehabilitation in neurological patients, among other themes.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/DSC00446.JPG\" style=\"width: 60%;\" /></p>\n<p>\n	Thanks for your time Esther!!!</p>\n<p>\n	You can see full interview, <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/English/#!/_536_1\">here</a></p>\n','INcite knowledge- Esther Udina','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-10-28','',0,NULL,2),(155,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	La passada setmana es varen comunicar els projectes amb &nbsp;finan&ccedil;ament de la darrera edici&oacute; de &quot;La Marat&oacute; de TV3&quot;, dedicada a les malalties neurodegeneratives. La UAB ha obtingut una part important, essent l&rsquo;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies una de les institucions beneficiades amb projectes.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.tv3.cat/marato/arxiu/2013/malalties\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/marato_desembre_2013.jpg\" style=\"width: 35%;\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	M&eacute;s informaci&oacute;, <a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/sala-de-premsa/detall-de-noticia/17-projectes-de-la-uab-i-de-l-8217-esfera-uab-cei-reben-4-milions-d-euros-de-la-marato-1345667174054.html?noticiaid=1345677403227\" target=\"_blank\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n','Atorgats els projectes de \"La Marató\"','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-11-03','',0,NULL,0),(156,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	La pasada semana se comunicaron los proyectos con financiaci&oacute;n de la &uacute;ltima edici&oacute;n de &ldquo;La Marat&oacute; de TV3&quot;, dedicada a las enfermedades neurodegenerativas. La UAB ha obtenido una parte importante, siendo el &quot;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies&quot; una de las instituciones beneficiadas con proyectos.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.tv3.cat/marato/arxiu/2013/malalties\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/marato_desembre_2013.jpg\" style=\"width: 35%;\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	M&aacute;s informaci&oacute;n, <a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/sala-de-premsa/detall-de-noticia/17-projectes-de-la-uab-i-de-l-8217-esfera-uab-cei-reben-4-milions-d-euros-de-la-marato-1345667174054.html?noticiaid=1345677403227\" target=\"_blank\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n','Otorgados los proyectos de \"La Marató\"','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-11-03','',0,NULL,1),(157,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Last week were reported the projects financed by the latest edition of &ldquo;La Marat&oacute; de TV3&rdquo; dedicated to neurodegenerative diseases. UAB has won an important part, with the &quot;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies&quot; as one of the institutions benefited with projects.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.tv3.cat/marato/arxiu/2013/malalties\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/marato_desembre_2013.jpg\" style=\"width: 35%;\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	More information, <a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/sala-de-premsa/detall-de-noticia/17-projectes-de-la-uab-i-de-l-8217-esfera-uab-cei-reben-4-milions-d-euros-de-la-marato-1345667174054.html?noticiaid=1345677403227\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></p>\n','Granted the projects of \"La Marató\"','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-11-03','',0,NULL,2),(158,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Ens plau anunciar-vos que el proper <strong>divendres 16 de gener de 2015</strong>, l&rsquo;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies acollir&agrave; la presentaci&oacute; a la UAB de la plataforma de crowdfunding cient&iacute;fic PRECIPITA. En temps dif&iacute;cils tamb&eacute; per a la ci&egrave;ncia, PRECIPITA es presenta com una alternativa que s&rsquo;est&agrave; demostrant molt v&agrave;lida, tant per a obtenir finan&ccedil;ament, com per apropar la ci&egrave;ncia al ciutad&agrave;.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.precipita.es/\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/logo_fondoVerde1.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Us esperem el 16/01/2015 a les 12h, a l&rsquo;aula Laia Acar&iacute;n M1/129 (cal confirmaci&oacute; pr&egrave;via enviant correu a <a href=\"mailto:web.inc@uab.cat\">web.inc@uab.cat</a> )</p>\n','Presentació de PRECIPITA: Crowdfunding científic','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-11-28','',0,NULL,0),(159,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Nos complace anunciar que el pr&oacute;ximo <strong>viernes 16 de enero de 2015</strong>, el &ldquo;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies&rdquo; acoger&aacute; la presentaci&oacute;n en la UAB de la plataforma crowdfunding cient&iacute;fico PRECIPITA. En tiempos dif&iacute;ciles tambi&eacute;n para la ciencia, PRECIPITA se presenta como una alternativa que se est&aacute; demostrando muy v&aacute;lida, tanto para la obtenci&oacute;n de financiaci&oacute;n, como para acercar la ciencia al ciudadano.</p>\n<p>\n	<a href=\"http://www.precipita.es/\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/logo_fondoVerde1.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	Os esperamos el 16/01/2015 a las 12h en el aula Laia Acar&iacute;n M1/129(es necesaria &nbsp;confirmaci&oacute;n previa enviando un correo a <a href=\"mailto:web.inc@uab.cat\">web.inc@uab.cat</a> )</p>\n','Presentación  de PRECIPITA: Crowdfunding cientifico','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-11-26','',0,NULL,1),(160,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	We are pleased to announce that on <strong>Friday 16th&nbsp; of January 2015</strong>, the &ldquo;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies&rdquo; &nbsp;will host the presentation of the scientific &nbsp;crowdfunding platform PRECIPITA &nbsp;at the UAB. In difficult times also for science PRECIPITA is presented as an alternative that is proving very useful, both to obtain funding and to bring science to the public.</p>\n<p>\n	<a href=\"http://www.precipita.es/\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/logo_fondoVerde1.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></a><br />\n	<br />\n	We expect to join us on 16.01.2015 at 12pm, at Laia Acar&iacute;ns classroom M1 / 129 (previous confirmation is needed by sending an email to <a href=\"mailto:web.inc@uab.cat\">web.inc@uab.cat</a> )</p>\n','Presentation of PRECIPITA: Scientific crowdfunding','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-11-26','',0,NULL,2),(161,NULL,'<p>\n	Aquest cop marxem cap a Psicobiologia, on l&#39;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies t&eacute; diversos grups de recerca.</p>\n<p>\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/DSC00475A.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></p>\n<p>\n	Veure entrevista completa <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Catala/#!/_534_1\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n<p>\n	Gr&agrave;cies Pol!</p>\n','Nova entrevista a la secció INcentivem el coneixement','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-12-10','',0,NULL,0),(162,NULL,'<p>\n	Esta vez nos vamos hacia Psicobiolog&iacute;a, donde el &quot;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies&quot; tiene diversos grupos de investigaci&oacute;n.</p>\n<p>\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/DSC00475A.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></p>\n<p>\n	Ver entrevista completa <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Castellano/#!/_535_1\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n<p>\n	Gracias Pol!</p>\n','Nueva entrevista en la sección INcentivemos el conocimiento','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-12-10','',0,NULL,1),(163,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	This time we are going to Psychobiology, where &quot;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies&quot; has different research groups.</p>\n<p>\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/DSC00475A.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></p>\n<p>\n	You can see full interview <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/English/#!/_536_1\">here</a></p>\n<p>\n	Thank you Pol!</p>\n','New interview in INcite\'s knowledge section','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-12-10','',0,NULL,2),(164,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	L&rsquo;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies ja disposa d&rsquo;espai propi al repositori p&uacute;blic de la UAB (<a href=\"http://ddd.uab.cat\" target=\"_blank\">DDD</a>), amb l&rsquo;alimentaci&oacute; d&rsquo;aquesta eina, molt ben posicionada a les recerques a internet, etc. es pret&eacute;n augmentar la visibilitat de la producci&oacute; cient&iacute;fica i la seva difusi&oacute;.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://ddd.uab.cat/collection/inc\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/DDD.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></a></p>\n','L’Institut de Neurociències amb col.lecció pròpia al Dipòsit Digital de Documents (DDD)','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-12-16','',0,NULL,0),(165,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	L&rsquo;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies ya dispone de espacio propio en el repositorio p&uacute;blico de la UAB (<a href=\"http://ddd.uab.cat\" target=\"_blank\">DDD</a>), con la alimentaci&oacute;n de esta herramienta, muy bien posicionada en las b&uacute;squedas en internet, etc. se pretende aumentar la visibilidad de la producci&oacute;n cient&iacute;fica y su difusi&oacute;n.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://ddd.uab.cat/collection/inc\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/DDD.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></a></p>\n','El Institut de Neurociències con colección propia en el Depósito Digital de Documentos (DDD)','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-12-16','',0,NULL,1),(166,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies has its own space inside the public repository of the UAB (<a href=\"http://ddd.uab.cat\" target=\"_blank\">DDD</a>); with the power of this internet well positioned tool, etc. the objective is to increase the visibility of the scientific production and its dissemination.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://ddd.uab.cat/collection/inc\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/DDD.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></a></p>\n','Institut de Neurociències with own collection in the Digital repository of Documents (DDD)','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2014-12-16','',0,NULL,2),(167,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	El Dr. Albert Quintana, <a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/sala-de-premsa/detall-de-noticia/tres-investigadors-de-la-uab-reconeguts-amb-starting-grants-1345667174054.html?noticiaid=1345679527238\" target=\"_blank\">un dels 3 guardonats de la UAB amb les &ldquo;Starting grants&rdquo; europees</a>, comen&ccedil;ar&agrave; a formar part de l&rsquo;INc i del Departament de Biologia Cel&middot;lular, Fisiologia i Immunologia , a partir del proper mes d&rsquo;abril, com a investigador <em>Ram&oacute;n y Cajal</em>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/quintana_romero.jpg\" style=\"width: 173px; height: 185px;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	El laboratori del Dr Quintana investiga els mecanismes moleculars que defineixen perqu&egrave; certes poblacions neuronals s&rsquo;afecten particularment pels trastorns mitocondrials, amb l&rsquo;objectiu final d&rsquo;identificar noves dianes que condueixin a tractaments millors pels pacients afectats de trastorns mitocondrials.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Li donem la benvinguda amb ell i al seu equip!!!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	M&eacute;s informaci&oacute; de la feina que desenvolupa <a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/QuintanalabCat(1).pdf\" target=\"_blank\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n','El Dr. Albert Quintana- Guardonat pel ERC (European Research Council), s’incorpora al Institut de Neurociències','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-01-12','',0,NULL,0),(168,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	El Dr. Albert Quintana, <a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/sala-de-premsa/detall-de-noticia/tres-investigadors-de-la-uab-reconeguts-amb-starting-grants-1345667174054.html?noticiaid=1345679527238\" target=\"_blank\">uno de los 3 galardonados en la UAB con las &ldquo;Starting grants&rdquo; europeas, </a>comenzar&aacute; a formar parte del INc y del Departamento de Biolog&iacute;a Celular, Fisiolog&iacute;a e Inmunolog&iacute;a, a partir del pr&oacute;ximo mes de abril, como investigador <em>Ram&oacute;n y Cajal</em>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/quintana_romero.jpg\" style=\"width: 173px; height: 185px;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	El laboratorio del Dr. Quintana investiga los mecanismos moleculares que definen porqu&eacute; ciertas poblaciones neuronales se afectan particularmente por los trastornos mitocondriales, con el objetivo final de identificar nuevas dianas que conduzcan a mejores tratamientos para los pacientes afectados de trastornos mitocondriales.</p>\n<p>\n	Le damos la bienvenida a &eacute;l y a su equipo!!!</p>\n<p>\n	M&aacute;s informaci&oacute;n del trabajo que desarrolla <a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/QuintanalabCast.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','Dr. Albert Quintana, galardonado por el ERC (European Research Council), se incorpora al “Institut de Neurociències”','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-01-12','',0,NULL,1),(169,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Dr. Albert Quintana, <a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/newsroom/news-detail-1345668003610.html?noticiaid=1345679527238\" target=\"_blank\">one of the three winners in the UAB with the European Starting Grants,</a> will begin to be part of INc and Department of Cell Biology, Physiology and Immunology, starting next April, as a researcher <em>Ram&oacute;n y Cajal</em>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/quintana_romero.jpg\" style=\"width: 173px; height: 185px;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	The&nbsp;Quintana lab&nbsp;investigates the molecular mechanisms defining why some neuronal populations are particularly affected by mitochondrial disease, with the overarching goal of identifying novel targets that lead to improved treatments for mitochondrial disease patients.</p>\n<p>\n	We welcome him and his team !!!</p>\n<p>\n	More information about the work that develops <a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/QuintanaLabEng.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','Dr Albert Quintana, awarded by the ERC (European Research Council), joins the “Institut de Neurociències”','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-01-12','',1,NULL,2),(170,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Un grup de recerca de l&rsquo;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies demostra en un estudi, l&rsquo;efic&agrave;cia de l&rsquo;estimulaci&oacute; intracranial per recuperar l&rsquo;aprenentatge i la mem&ograve;ria en rates.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/PSegdef.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Podeu consultar la not&iacute;cia <a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/sala-de-premsa/detall-de-noticia/demostren-l-8217-eficacia-de-l-8217-estimulacio-intracranial-per-recuperar-l-8217-aprenentatge-i-la-memoria-en-rates-1345667174054.html?noticiaid=1345680639915\" target=\"_blank\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n','Estudi sobre l\'estimulació intracranial','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-01-28','',0,NULL,0),(171,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Un grupo de investigaci&oacute;n del <em>Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</em> demuestra en un estudio, la eficacia de la estimulaci&oacute;n intracraneal para recuperar el aprendizaje y la memoria en ratas.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/PSegdef.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Consultar not&iacute;cia completa <a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/sala-de-prensa/detalle-noticia-1345667994339.html?noticiaid=1345680639915\" target=\"_blank\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n','Estudio sobre la estimulación intracraneal','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-01-28','',0,NULL,1),(172,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	A research group at the Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies demonstrates in a study, the efficacy of intracranial stimulation to restore learning and memory in rats.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/PSegdef.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	More information<a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/newsroom/news-detail-1345668003610.html?noticiaid=1345680639915\" target=\"_blank\"> here</a></p>\n','Intracranial stimulation study','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-01-28','',0,NULL,2),(173,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Aquesta&nbsp; setmana s&rsquo;han obert les inscripcions per al proper Congr&eacute;s sobre la Glia a Sydney, que es dur&agrave; a terme durant el mes d&rsquo;agost d&rsquo;enguany i on l&rsquo;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies ha contribu&iuml;t, entre d&rsquo;altres coses, aportant recursos per atorgar beques als estudiants que hi vulguin assistir.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://sydneygliameeting.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/SydneyGlia.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Podeu registrar-vos clicant <a href=\"http://sydneygliameeting.com/registration.html\" target=\"_blank\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n','Obertura d’inscripcions per al Sydney Glia meeting d’Austràlia','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-01-30','',0,NULL,0),(174,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Esta semana se han abierto las inscripciones para el pr&oacute;ximo Congreso sobre la Glia en Sydney, que se llevar&aacute; a cabo durante el mes de agosto de este a&ntilde;o y donde el &nbsp;<em>Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</em> ha contribuido, entre otras cosas, aportando recursos para otorgar becas a los estudiantes que quieran asistir.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://sydneygliameeting.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/SydneyGlia.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Para registro, clic <a href=\"http://sydneygliameeting.com/registration.html\" target=\"_blank\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n','Obertura de inscripciones para el Sydney Glia meeting en Australia','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-01-30','',0,NULL,1),(175,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	This week was opened registration for the next Congress on Glia in Sydney, which will be held during August this year and where the <em>Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</em> has contributed, among other things, providing resources to grant scholarships for students who wish to attend.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://sydneygliameeting.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/SydneyGlia.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	For registration click <a href=\"http://sydneygliameeting.com/registration.html\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></p>\n','Opening registration for the Sydney Glia meeting in Australia','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-01-30','',0,NULL,2),(176,NULL,'<p>\n	En aquesta nova entrevista, el David Torrents ens explica una mica el seu dia a dia dins la branca de Psicologia M&egrave;dica. No us ho perdeu!<br />\n	<br />\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/DTorrents1.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></p>\n<p>\n	Gr&agrave;cies David!</p>\n<p>\n	Entrevista completa <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Catala/#!/_534_1\">aqu&iacute;</a><br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','Incentivem el coneixement: Psicologia Mèdica','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-02-02','',0,NULL,0),(177,NULL,'<p>\n	En esta nueva entrevista, David Torrents nos explica un poco su d&iacute;a a d&iacute;a dentro de la rama de la Psicolog&iacute;a M&eacute;dica. No os lo perdais!<br />\n	<br />\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/DTorrents1.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></p>\n<p>\n	Gracias David!</p>\n<p>\n	Entrevista completa <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Castellano/#!/_535_1\">aqu&iacute;</a><br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','INcentivemos el conocimiento: Psicología Médica','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-02-02','',0,NULL,1),(178,NULL,'<p>\n	<span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">In this new</span> <span class=\"hps\">interview,</span> <span class=\"hps\">David</span> <span class=\"hps\">Torrents </span><span class=\"hps alt-edited\">explains us</span> <span class=\"hps alt-edited\">a little</span> <span class=\"hps\">in</span> <span class=\"hps\">their day to</span> <span class=\"hps\">day</span> <span class=\"hps\">branch</span> <span class=\"hps\">of</span> <span class=\"hps\">Medical Psychology</span><span>.</span> <span class=\"hps\">Do not miss it</span><span>!</span></span><br />\n	<br />\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/DTorrents1.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></p>\n<p>\n	Thank you David!</p>\n<p>\n	Full interview <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/English/#!/_536_1\">here</a></p>\n','INcite knowledge: Medical Psychology','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-02-02','',0,NULL,2),(179,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Ens plau presentar-vos les activitats que el nostre institut dur&agrave; a terme enguany, tant per a centres educatius com per al p&uacute;blic en general, esperem us siguin d&#39;inter&egrave;s. Feli&ccedil; neuroci&egrave;ncia!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/PosterBAWinc2015web3.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/PosterBAWinc2015web3.jpg\" style=\"width: 60%;\" /></a></p>\n','Activitats de l\' Institut de Neurociències per a la Setmana del Cervell 2015','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-02-11','',0,NULL,0),(180,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"es\"><span class=\"hps\">Nos complace</span> <span class=\"hps\">presentar las</span> <span class=\"hps\">actividades</span> <span class=\"hps\">que nuestro</span> <span class=\"hps\">instituto</span> <span class=\"hps\">llevar&aacute; a</span> <span class=\"hps\">cabo este a&ntilde;o</span><span>, tanto</span> <span class=\"hps\">para centros</span> <span class=\"hps\">educativos</span> <span class=\"hps\">como para el</span> <span class=\"hps\">p&uacute;blico en general,</span> <span class=\"hps\">esperamos que sean</span> <span class=\"hps\">de inter&eacute;s</span>. Feliz neurociencia!</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/PosterBAWinc2015web3.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/PosterBAWinc2015web3.jpg\" style=\"width: 60%;\" /></a></p>\n','Actividades del Institut de Neurociències para la Semana del cerebro 2015','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-02-11','',0,NULL,1),(181,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"es\"><span class=\"hps\"><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">We are</span> <span class=\"hps\">pleased to present</span> <span class=\"hps\">our</span> <span class=\"hps\">institute</span> <span class=\"hps\">activities</span> <span class=\"hps\">carried out</span> <span class=\"hps\">this year</span><span>, both for</span> <span class=\"hps\">schools</span> <span class=\"hps\">and for&nbsp;</span> <span class=\"hps\">general public</span><span>, we hope</span> <span class=\"hps\">you find them</span> <span class=\"hps\">interesting. Happy neuroscience!!!</span> </span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/PosterBAWinc2015web3.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/PosterBAWinc2015web3.jpg\" style=\"width: 60%;\" /></a></p>\n','Activities of the Institut de Neurociències for the Brain awareness week 2015','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-02-11','',0,NULL,2),(182,NULL,'<p>\n	La vicedirectora i investigadora de l&#39;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies <a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(261,1);\">Roser Nadal Alemany</a>, ha estat guardonada amb el premi <a href=\"https://www.icrea.cat/Web/Awarded.aspx\" target=\"_blank\