dos? A cargo del Dr. Alfredo Mi&ntilde;ano<br />\n	19.15h- Charla: Psicof&aacute;rmacos&nbsp; buenos y psicof&aacute;rmacos malos. A cargo del Dr. Jordi Ortiz</p>\n<p>\n	Exhibici&oacute;n temporal de neurojoias a cargo del Dr. Bernardo Castellano.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://neurojewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/neurojewelryWeb.jpg\" style=\"width: 30%;\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	Todas las actividades se llevaran a cabo en el&nbsp; <a href=\"https://plus.google.com/100282530115268148827/about?gl=es&amp;hl=es\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Museu d&rsquo;Art de Cerdanyola. Can Dom&egrave;nech</em></a></p>\n','Semana del Cerebro 2015- Reseña y próximas actividades','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-03-17','',1,NULL,1),(197,NULL,'<p>\n	Great review of&nbsp; <a href=\"http://cerdanyola.info/\" target=\"_blank\">Cerdanyola.info</a> about <em>Cells on Canvas</em> exhibition in the MAC:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://cerdanyola.info/societat/lart-i-la-ciencia-es-donen-la-ma-en-una-exposicio-al-mac/\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/CellsOnCanvas1web.jpg\" style=\"width: 30%;\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	Upcoming activities for all ages on the occasion of Brain Awareness Week:</p>\n<p>\n	- March, Friday20th -<br />\n	17.30h- Talk: How to store memories? By Dr. Alfredo Mi&ntilde;ano<br />\n	19.15h- Talk:Good and bad psychotropic drugs. By Dr. Jordi Ortiz</p>\n<p>\n	Temporary exhibition of neurojewelry by Dr. Bernardo Castellano</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://neurojewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/neurojewelryWeb.jpg\" style=\"width: 30%;\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	All activities will be held at the &nbsp; <a href=\"https://plus.google.com/100282530115268148827/about?gl=es&amp;hl=es\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Museu d&rsquo;Art de Cerdanyola. Can Dom&egrave;nech</em></a></p>\n','Brain awareness week: Review and next activities','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-03-17','',1,NULL,2),(200,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Once the Brain Awareness Week 2015 is finished, we can only thank the participation and collaboration, both members of the INc: Carlos Barcia, Bernardo Castellano, Igor Ivan Cigarroa, Gemma Guillazo, Alfredo Mi&ntilde;ano, Jordi Ortiz, Anna Vale; as institutions that have received us: City Council of Barcelona, City Council of Cerdanyola, Cerdanyola Art Museum (MAC) and School Bellaterra.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	We are already thinking about next year!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/BAW2015BCN.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/BAW2015BCN.jpg\" style=\"width: 60%;\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:9px;\"><em>Activity: The Illusion of what we see- Schools of Barcelona</em></span></p>\n','Thank you!','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-03-23','',0,NULL,2),(201,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Un cop finalitzada la Setmana del Cervell 2015, nom&eacute;s ens queda agrair la participaci&oacute; i col&middot;laboraci&oacute;, tant dels membres de l&rsquo;INc: Carlos Barcia, Bernardo Castellano, Igor Ivan Cigarroa, Gemma Guillazo, Alfredo Mi&ntilde;ano, Jordi Ortiz, Anna Vale; com de les institucions que ens han acollit: Ajuntament de Barcelona, Ajuntament de Cerdanyola, Museu d&rsquo;Art de Cerdanyola i Escola Bellaterra.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Ja pensem en el proper any!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/BAW2015BCN.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/BAW2015BCN.jpg\" style=\"width: 60%;\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:9px;\"><em>Activitat: La il.lusi&oacute; del que veiem- Escoles de Barcelona</em></span></p>\n','Gràcies!','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-03-23','',0,NULL,0),(202,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Una vez finalizada la Semana del Cerebro 2015, solamente nos queda agradecer la participaci&oacute;n y colaboraci&oacute;n, tanto de los miembros del INc: Carlos Barcia, Bernardo Castellano, Igor Ivan Cigarroa, Gemma Guillazo, Alfredo Mi&ntilde;ano, Jordi Ortiz, Anna Vale; como a las instituciones que nos han acogido: Ayuntamiento de Barcelona, Ayuntamiento de Cerdanyola, Museo de Arte de Cerdanyola (MAC) y escuela Bellaterra.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Ya pensamos en el pr&oacute;ximo a&ntilde;o!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/BAW2015BCN.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/BAW2015BCN.jpg\" style=\"width: 60%;\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:9px;\"><em>Actividad: La ilusi&oacute;n de lo que vemos- Escuelas de Barcelona</em></span></p>\n','Gracias!','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-03-23','',0,NULL,1),(203,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Aquest cop, membres de l&rsquo;<em>Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</em> impartiran un curs titulat: <em>Neuroci&egrave;ncia i emocions</em>, que inspeccionar&agrave; les arrels i or&iacute;gens de les nostres emocions. El curs est&agrave; coordinat per la <a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(271,1); \"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Dra. Lydia Gimenez</span></a> i es pot trobar a l&rsquo;oferta&nbsp; dels centres c&iacute;vics Casa Elizalde i Casa Golferichs.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"http://www.casaelizalde.com/cursos/destaquem/neurociencia-i-emocions/\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"74\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/LogoElizalde.gif\" width=\"72\" /></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"https://inscripcions.golferichs.org/ccivic/activitats.xml\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/golferichs.jpg\" style=\"width: 180px; height: 52px;\" /></a></p>\n','Nou curs sobre la Neurociència als Centres cívics de Barcelona','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-03-23','',0,NULL,0),(204,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Esta vez, miembros del <em>Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</em> impartir&aacute;n un curso titulado: <em>Neurociencia y emociones</em>, que inspeccionar&aacute; las ra&iacute;ces y or&iacute;genes de nuestras emociones. El curso est&aacute; coordinado por la <a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(452,1); \"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Dra. Lydia Gimenez</span></a> y se puede encontrar en la oferta de los centros c&iacute;vicos Casa Elizalde y Casa Golferichs.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"http://www.casaelizalde.com/cursos/destaquem/neurociencia-i-emocions/\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"74\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/LogoElizalde.gif\" width=\"72\" /></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"https://inscripcions.golferichs.org/ccivic/activitats.xml\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/golferichs.jpg\" style=\"width: 180px; height: 52px;\" /></a></p>\n','Nuevo curso de neurociencia en centros cívicos de Barcelona','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-03-23','',0,NULL,1),(205,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	This time, members of the del <em>Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</em> will lecture a course entitled: <em>Neuroscience and emotions</em>, which will inspect the roots and origins of our emotions. The course is coordinated by <a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(419,1); \"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Dr. Lydia Gimenez </span></a>and can be found in the course offering at community centers Casa Elizalde and Casa Golferichs.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"http://www.casaelizalde.com/cursos/destaquem/neurociencia-i-emocions/\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"74\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/LogoElizalde.gif\" width=\"72\" /></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"https://inscripcions.golferichs.org/ccivic/activitats.xml\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/golferichs.jpg\" style=\"width: 180px; height: 52px;\" /></a></p>\n','New course of neuroscience at community centers in Barcelona','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-03-23','',0,NULL,2),(206,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	La nostra estimada Cristina viatjava a l&rsquo;avi&oacute; que volava des de Barcelona a D&uuml;sseldorf. La Cristina ha estat membre del nostre Institut des del 2006 al 2011, i la seva p&egrave;rdua ens deixa un gran dolor. Hem perdut un &agrave;ngel. No tenim paraules.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/Cristina-Mweb.jpg\" style=\"width: 60%;\" /></p>\n','In Memoriam Cristina Muñoz Abellán (1982-2015)','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-03-26','',0,NULL,0),(207,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Nuestra estimada Cristina viajaba en el avi&oacute;n que volaba desde Barcelona a D&uuml;sseldorf. Cristina fue miembro de nuestro Instituto desde 2006 al 2011, y su p&eacute;rdida nos sumerge en el dolor. Hemos perdido un &aacute;ngel. No tenemos palabras.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/Cristina-Mweb.jpg\" style=\"width: 60%;\" /></p>\n','In Memoriam Cristina Muñoz Abellán (1982-2015)','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-03-26','',0,NULL,1),(208,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Our beloved Cristina was traveling on the plane flying from Barcelona to D&uuml;sseldorf. Cristina was a member of our Institute from 2006 to 2011, and its loss immerses us in sorrow. We lost an angel. We have no words.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/Cristina-Mweb.jpg\" style=\"width: 60%;\" /></p>\n','In Memoriam Cristina Muñoz Abellán (1982-2015)','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-03-26','',0,NULL,2),(209,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	L&rsquo;ag&egrave;ncia Europea del Medicament acaba d&rsquo;aprovar l&rsquo;&uacute;s del f&agrave;rmac ABTL0812 per comen&ccedil;ar els assajos pel&nbsp; tractament del c&agrave;ncer infantil neuroblastoma.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Aquest f&agrave;rmac ha estat desenvolupat per <a href=\"http://www.abilitypharma.com/EN/13/main-menu/about-ab-therapeutics.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Ability Pharmaceuticals</span></a> en estreta col.laboraci&oacute; amb el grup de recerca del <a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(276,1); \"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Dr. Jose Miguel Lizcano</span></a>, (coordinador del grup <em>Cell Signaling mechanisms in health and metabolic, mental and cancer diseases</em>) entre d&#39;altres. Al 2014 es varen iniciar els primers assajos amb ABTL0812 en pacients amb c&agrave;ncer avan&ccedil;at i al 2015 s&#39;iniciar&agrave; la fase cl&iacute;nica II.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	El neuroblastoma es un c&agrave;ncer poc com&uacute; del sistema nervi&oacute;s que afecta a nens i nadons, i causa al voltant d&rsquo;un 15% de les morts relacionades amb c&agrave;ncer als nens.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	M&eacute;s informaci&oacute; <a href=\"http://www.lavanguardia.com/vida/20150407/54429463452/ensayan-un-farmaco-para-tratar-el-cancer-infantil-neuroblastoma.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">aqu&iacute;</span></a></p>\n','Investigadors del INc i l\'empresa Ability Pharmaceuticals del Parc de Recerca UAB aconsegueixen l\'aprovació d\'un fàrmac pel tractament del càncer infantil neuroblastoma','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-04-09','',0,NULL,0),(210,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	La agencia Europea del Medicamento acaba de aprobar el uso del f&agrave;rmaco ABTL0812 para comenzar los ensayos para el tratamiento del c&aacute;ncer infantil neuroblastoma.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Este f&aacute;rmaco ha sido desarrollado por <a href=\"http://www.abilitypharma.com/EN/13/main-menu/about-ab-therapeutics.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Ability Pharmaceuticals</span></a><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span>en estrecha colaboraci&oacute;n con el grupo de investigaci&oacute;n del&nbsp; <a href=\"javascript:MostraPage(457,1); \"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Dr. Jos&eacute; Miguel Lizcano</span></a>, (coordinador del grupo Cell Signaling mechanisms in health and metabolic, mental and cancer diseases) entre otros. En 2014 se iniciaron los primeros ensayos con ABTL0812 en pacientes con c&aacute;ncer avanzado y el 2015 se iniciar&aacute; la fase cl&iacute;nica II.&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	El neuroblastoma es un c&aacute;ncer poco com&uacute;n del sistema nervioso que afecta a ni&ntilde;os y beb&eacute;s y causa alrededor de un 15% de las muertes relacionadas con c&aacute;ncer infantil.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	M&aacute;s informaci&oacute;n <a href=\"http://www.lavanguardia.com/vida/20150407/54429463452/ensayan-un-farmaco-para-tratar-el-cancer-infantil-neuroblastoma.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">aqu&iacute;</span></a></p>\n','Investigadores del INc y la empresa Ability Pharmaceuticals del Parc de Recerca UAB consiguen la aprobación de un fármaco para el tratamiento del cáncer infantil neuroblastoma','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-04-09','',0,NULL,1),(211,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	The European Medicines Agency has just approved the use of the drug: ABTL0812 to begin trials for the treatment of childhood cancer neuroblastoma.<br />\n	<br />\n	This drug has been developed by <a href=\"http://www.abilitypharma.com/EN/13/main-menu/about-ab-therapeutics.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Ability Pharmaceuticals</span></a> in close collaboration with the research group of <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/English/index.php#!/Investigators_353_1\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Dr. Jose Miguel Lizcano</span></a>, (group coordinator&nbsp; of Cell Signaling mechanisms in health and metabolic, cancer and mental diseases) among others. In 2014 they began the first trials in patients with advanced cancer ABTL0812 and in 2015 will begin the clinical phase II.<br />\n	<br />\n	Neuroblastoma is a rare cancer that affects the nervous system in newborn and children, and cause about 15% of cancer-related deaths in children.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	More information <a href=\"http://www.lavanguardia.com/vida/20150407/54429463452/ensayan-un-farmaco-para-tratar-el-cancer-infantil-neuroblastoma.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">here</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','INc Researchers and the company Ability Pharmaceuticals of Parc de Recerca UAB get the approval of a drug for the treatment of childhood cancer neuroblastoma','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-04-09','',0,NULL,2),(212,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Aprofitem la propera Diada de Sant Jordi per a recomanar-vos el <strong>NOU</strong> llibre del nostre company el <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Catala/index.php#!/Pilar-SEGURA_288_1\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Dr. Ignacio Morgado</span></a>. Aquest cop ens dona detalls en format de petites c&agrave;psules, per a con&egrave;ixer millor el nostre cervell.</p>\n<p>\n	Podeu llegir-ne un fragment clicant aqu&iacute;:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/29749_La_fabrica_ilusiones.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/29749_La_fabrica_ilusionesPORTADA.JPG\" style=\"width: 60%;\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','Una especial recomanació per a la Diada de Sant Jordi','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-04-20','',0,NULL,0),(213,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Aprovechamos la pr&oacute;xima <em>Diada de Sant Jordi</em> para recomendar el <strong>NUEVO</strong> libro de nuestro compa&ntilde;ero el <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Castellano/index.php#!/Pilar-Segura_468_1\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Dr. Ignacio Morgado</span></a>. Esta vez con m&aacute;s&nbsp; detalles para conocer mejor nuestro cerebro, &nbsp;en formato de peque&ntilde;as c&aacute;psulas</p>\n<p>\n	Leer un fragmento clicando aqu&iacute;:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/29749_La_fabrica_ilusiones.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/29749_La_fabrica_ilusionesPORTADA.JPG\" style=\"width: 60%;\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','Una especial recomendación para Sant Jordi','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-04-20','',0,NULL,1),(214,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps alt-edited\">Taking advantage of</span> <span class=\"hps\">the next</span> <em><span class=\"hps\">Diada de Sant Jordi</span></em> <span class=\"hps\">we recommend the</span> <span class=\"hps\"><strong>NEW </strong>book by</span> <span class=\"hps\">our colleague</span> <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/English/index.php#!/Pilar-Segura_435_1\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span class=\"hps\">Dr.</span> <span class=\"hps\">Ignacio</span> <span class=\"hps\">Morgado</span></span></a><span>.</span> <span class=\"hps\">This time</span> <span class=\"hps\">is giving details</span> <span class=\"hps alt-edited\">to learn more about</span> <span class=\"hps\">our brain,</span> <span class=\"hps alt-edited\">in the format of</span> <span class=\"hps\">small capsules</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span class=\"short_text\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">Read</span> <span class=\"hps\">an excerpt</span> <span class=\"hps\">clicking here</span><span>:</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/29749_La_fabrica_ilusiones.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/29749_La_fabrica_ilusionesPORTADA.JPG\" style=\"width: 60%;\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','An special recommendation for Sant Jordi Day (Saint George)','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-04-20','',0,NULL,2),(215,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Amb la primavera, l&#39;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies augmenta de nou la seva programaci&oacute; de seminaris al mes de maig amb la visita del <a href=\"http://bearlab-s1.mit.edu/BearLab/people/bosch.html\" target=\"_blank\">Dr. Miquel Bosch</a> (MIT) i el <a href=\"http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/\" target=\"_blank\">Dr. Mauricio R. Papini </a>(Texas Christian University), convidat aquest &uacute;ltim en coordinaci&oacute; amb el <a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/core-salut/\" target=\"_blank\">CORE de Salut Mental de la UAB.</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/Mbosch.jpg\" style=\"width: 130px; height: 143px;\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img alt=\"\" height=\"143\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/MRPapini.jpg\" width=\"156\" /></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:10px;\"><em>Dr. Miquel Bosch &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:10px;\"><em>Dr. Mauricio R. Papini &nbsp;&nbsp;</em></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	Consulteu dates i programaci&oacute; anual <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Catala/Documents/SEMINARIS%20INc%202015V4.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">aqu&iacute; &nbsp;&nbsp;</a></p>\n<p>\n	Consulteu abstract del Dr. Bosch <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Catala/#!/Activitats_532_1\" target=\"_blank\">aqu&iacute; </a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n','Seminaris extraordinaris de primavera!','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-04-30','',1,NULL,0),(216,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Con la primavera, l&rsquo;<em>Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</em> aumenta de nuevo su programaci&oacute;n de seminarios en el mes de mayo con la visita del <a href=\"http://bearlab-s1.mit.edu/BearLab/people/bosch.html\" target=\"_blank\">Dr. Miquel Bosch</a> (MIT) y el <a href=\"http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/\" target=\"_blank\">Dr. Mauricio R. Papini </a>(Texas Christian University), invitado en coordinaci&oacute;n con el <a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/investigar/itinerarios/la-investigacion/comunidades-de-investigacion-estrategica-cores-/presentacion-1345671281318.html?param1=1345668236617\" target=\"_blank\">CORE de Salut Mental de la UAB.</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/Mbosch.jpg\" style=\"width: 130px; height: 143px;\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img alt=\"\" height=\"143\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/MRPapini.jpg\" width=\"156\" /></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:10px;\"><em>Dr. Miquel Bosch &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:10px;\"><em>Dr. Mauricio R. Papini &nbsp;&nbsp;</em></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	Consultar fechas y programaci&oacute;n anual <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Castellano/Documents/SEMINARIS%20INc%202015V4.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n<p>\n	Consultar abstract del Dr. Bosch <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Castellano/#!/Actividades_531_1\" target=\"_blank\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','Seminarios extraordinarios de primavera!','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-04-30','',1,NULL,1),(217,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	With the spring, <em>Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</em> again increases its program of seminars in May with the visit of <a href=\"http://bearlab-s1.mit.edu/BearLab/people/bosch.html\" target=\"_blank\">Dr. Miquel Bosch</a> (MIT) and <a href=\"http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/\">Dr. Mauricio R. Papini </a>(Texas Christian University),invited in coordination with <a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/research/itineraries/uab-research/strategic-research-communities-cores-/introduction-1345671281322.html?param1=1345668236617\" target=\"_blank\">Strategic Research Community in Mental Health.</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/Mbosch.jpg\" style=\"width: 130px; height: 143px;\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img alt=\"\" height=\"143\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/MRPapini.jpg\" width=\"156\" /></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:10px;\"><em>Dr. Miquel Bosch &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:10px;\"><em>Dr. Mauricio R. Papini &nbsp;&nbsp;</em></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	Check dates and annual programming <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/English/Documents/SEMINARIS%20INc%202015V4.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">here</span></a></p>\n<p>\n	See Dr. Bosch abstract <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/English/#!/Activities_530_1\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">here</span></a></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n','Extra spring seminars!','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-04-30','',1,NULL,2),(218,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	El Dr Mauricio R. Papini (Department of Psychology, <a href=\"http://www.tcu.edu/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Texas Christian University</span></a>, USA), &eacute;s un <a href=\"http://www.fulbright.es/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Professor Visitant Fulbright</span></a>, que estar&agrave; en el nostre Institut entre el 25 i el 28 de Maig. Impartir&agrave; <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Catala/#!/Activitats_532_1\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">dues confer&egrave;ncies</span></a>, el 26 i el 27 de Maig, coorganitzades pel nostre Institut i per la <a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/core-salut/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">CORE Salut Mental UAB.</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/MRPapini.jpg\" style=\"width: 25%;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	El Profesor Papini est&agrave; interessat en la <em>Neuroci&egrave;ncia Comparada de l&rsquo;ansietat i la frustraci&oacute;</em>; &eacute;s a dir, en els mecanismes activats en situacions que suposen la p&egrave;rdua sobtada de recompensa. Aquesta p&egrave;rdua &eacute;s una font de modulaci&oacute; emocional que pot suposar supressi&oacute; conductual, inducci&oacute; de conductes motivades, canvis en la conducta agon&iacute;stica, alliberaci&oacute; d&rsquo;hormones d&rsquo;estr&egrave;s, modulaci&oacute; de la sensibilitat al dolor, i consum de subst&agrave;ncies amb potencial addictiu.&nbsp; Alguns dels mecanismes subjacents a l&rsquo;ajustament davant la p&egrave;rdua sobtada de recompensa se suposa que s&oacute;n distintius dels mam&iacute;fers. La <em>recerca comparada</em> indica que el tipus d&rsquo;ajustaments observats en vertebrats m&eacute;s primitius s&oacute;n &uacute;nicament cognitius, sense el to emocional comunament observat en experiments similars en mam&iacute;fers. L&rsquo;objectiu d&rsquo;aquesta recerca &eacute;s contribuir a un coneixement millor de l&rsquo;<a href=\"http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/papinipr02.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><em>evoluci&oacute; dels mecanismes d&rsquo;aprenentatge</em></span></a>, de la<em> <a href=\"http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/papinibbe03.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">connexi&oacute; entre l&rsquo;aprenentatge i l&rsquo;emoci&oacute;</span></a></em>, i de les <a href=\"http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/15papinin&amp;br.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><em>bases neurobiol&ograve;giques dels trastorns d&rsquo;ansietat.</em></span></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Key Reference</strong>:</span> Papini, M. R., Fuchs, P. N., &amp; Torres, C. (2015). Behavioral neuroscience of psychological pain. <em>Neuroscience &amp; Biobehavioral Reviews, 48</em>, 53-69.</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>CV <span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Complet:</strong></span></strong></span></p>\n<p>\n	<a href=\"http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/CompleteCV.pdf\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/CompleteCV.pdf</strong></span></a></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>More information:</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n	<a href=\"http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/index.htm\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/index.htm</strong></span></a></p>\n<p>\n	<em>Inc-Core Salut Mental UAB talks</em></p>\n','Visita del Dr. Mauricio R. Papini','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-05-08','',0,NULL,0),(219,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	El Dr. Mauricio R. Papini (Department of Psychology, <a href=\"http://www.tcu.edu/\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Texas Christian University, USA</span></a>), es un <a href=\"http://www.fulbright.es/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Profesor Visitante Fulbright</span></a>, que estar&aacute; en nuestro Instituto entre el 25 y 28 de mayo. Impartir&aacute; dos conferencias, el 26 y 27 de Mayo, coorganizadas por nuestro Instituto y por la <a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/investigar/itinerarios/la-investigacion/comunidades-de-investigacion-estrategica-cores-/presentacion-1345671281318.html?param1=1345668236617\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">CORE Salud Mental UAB.</span></a><br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/MRPapini.jpg\" style=\"width: 25%;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	El profesor Papini est&aacute; interesado en la <em>Neurociencia comparada de la ansiedad y la frustraci&oacute;n</em>; es decir, en los mecanismos activados en situaciones que suponen una p&eacute;rdida s&uacute;bita de recompensa. Esta p&eacute;rdida es una fuente de modulaci&oacute;n emocional que puede suponer supresi&oacute;n conductual, inducci&oacute;n de conductas motivadas, cambios en las conductas agon&iacute;sticas, liberaci&oacute;n de hormones de estr&eacute;s, modulaci&oacute;n de la sensibilidad al dolor, y consumo de sustancias con potencial adictivo. Algunos de los mecanismos subyacentes a&nbsp; los ajustes delante de la p&eacute;rdida s&uacute;bita de recompensa se supone que son distintivos de los mam&iacute;feros. La <em>investigaci&oacute;n comparada</em> indica que el tipo de ajustes observados en vertebrados m&aacute;s primitivas son &uacute;nicamente cognitivos, sin el tono emocional com&uacute;nmente observado en experimentos similares en mam&iacute;feros. El objetivo de esta investigaci&oacute;n es contribuir a un mejor conocimiento de la <a href=\"http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/papinipr02.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><em>evoluci&oacute;n de los mecanismos de aprendizaje</em></span></a>, de la <a href=\"http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/papinibbe03.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><em>conexi&oacute;n del aprendizaje y la emoci&oacute;n</em></span></a>, y de las<a href=\"http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/15papinin&amp;br.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> <em>bases neurobiol&oacute;gicas de los trastornos de ansiedad</em>.</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Key Reference</strong>:</span> Papini, M. R., Fuchs, P. N., &amp; Torres, C. (2015). Behavioral neuroscience of psychological pain. <em>Neuroscience &amp; Biobehavioral Reviews, 48</em>, 53-69.</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>CV <span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Completo:</strong></span></strong></span></p>\n<p>\n	<a href=\"http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/CompleteCV.pdf\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/CompleteCV.pdf</strong></span></a></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>M&aacute;s informaci&oacute;n:</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n	<a href=\"http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/index.htm\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/index.htm</strong></span></a></p>\n<p>\n	<em>Inc-Core Salut Mental UAB talks</em></p>\n','Visita del profesor Mauricio R. Papini','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-05-08','',0,NULL,1),(220,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Dr Mauricio R. Papini (Department of Psychology, <a href=\"http://www.tcu.edu/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Texas Christian University</span></a>, USA), as a <a href=\"http://www.fulbright.es/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Fulbright Visiting Professor</span></a>, will be in our Institute between May 25-28<sup>th</sup>. He will give two different lectures, the 26<sup>th</sup> and 27<sup>th</sup> of May, coorganized by our Institute and the <a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/research/itineraries/uab-research/strategic-research-communities-cores-/introduction-1345671281322.html?param1=1345668236617\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">CORE Salut Mental UAB</span></a><span style=\"color:#000000;\">.</span><br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/MRPapini.jpg\" style=\"width: 25%;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Prof Papini is interested in the <em>Comparative Neuroscience of anxiety and frustration</em>, that is, the mechanisms engaged in situations involving surprising reward loss. Surprising reward loss is a source of emotional modulation that can lead to behavioral suppression, drive induction, changes in agonistic behavior, release of stress hormones, modulation of pain sensitivity, and consumption of substances with addictive potential. Some of the mechanisms underlying adjustment to unexpected reward loss are hypothesized to be unique to mammals. <em>Comparative research</em> indicates that the type of adjustment observed in relatively more conservative vertebrates is purely cognitive, lacking the emotional tone commonly observed in analogous experiments with mammals. The goal of this research is to contribute to a better understanding of the <span style=\"color:#000000;\"><em><a href=\"http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/papinipr02.pdf\">evolution of learning mechanisms</a></em></span>, the <span style=\"color:#000000;\"><em><a href=\"http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/papinibbe03.pdf\">interface between learning and emotion</a></em></span>, and the <span style=\"color:#000000;\"><em><a href=\"http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/15papinin&amp;br.pdf\">neurobehavioral basis of anxiety disorders</a></em></span><em><span style=\"color:#000000;\">.</span></em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Key Reference</strong>:</span> Papini, M. R., Fuchs, P. N., &amp; Torres, C. (2015). Behavioral neuroscience of psychological pain. <em>Neuroscience &amp; Biobehavioral Reviews, 48</em>, 53-69.</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>Complet CV:</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n	<a href=\"http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/CompleteCV.pdf\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/CompleteCV.pdf</strong></span></a></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"color:#800000;\"><strong>More information:</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n	<a href=\"http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/index.htm\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>http://personal.tcu.edu/papini/index.htm</strong></span></a></p>\n<p>\n	<em>Inc-Core Salut Mental UAB talks</em></p>\n','Professor Mauricio R. Papini visit','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-05-08','',0,NULL,2),(221,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Voleu saber que es fa a Farmacologia? Nova entrega d&rsquo; Incentivem el coneixement amb la Dra. Vict&ograve;ria Clos.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/VClosWeb.jpg\" style=\"width: 60%;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Gr&agrave;cies per participar Vict&ograve;ria!!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Podeu llegir l&#39;entrevista complerta <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Catala/index.php#!/_534_1\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n','INcentivem el coneixement: Dra. Victòria Clos','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-05-18','',0,NULL,0),(222,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&iquest;Quer&eacute;is saber que se hace en Farmacolog&iacute;a? Nueva entrega de INcentivemos el conocimiento con la Dra Victoria Clos.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/VClosWeb.jpg\" style=\"width: 60%;\" /></p>\n<p>\n	Gracias por participar Victoria!!</p>\n<p>\n	Leer entrevista completa <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Castellano/#!/_535_1\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','INcentivemos el conocimiento: Dra Victoria Clos','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-05-18','',0,NULL,1),(223,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Do you wish to know what &nbsp;is done in Pharmacology ? New release of INcitate Knowledge with Dr. Victoria Clos.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<br />\n	<br />\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/VClosWeb.jpg\" style=\"width: 60%;\" /><br />\n	<br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	Thank you for participating Victoria!!</p>\n<p>\n	Read full interview <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/English/#!/_536_1\">here</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','INcite Knowledge: Dr. Victoria Clos','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-05-18','',0,NULL,2),(224,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Informaci&oacute; sobre els diferents t&ograve;pics a publicar el proper mes de setembre, criteris d&rsquo;avaluaci&oacute; i consells pr&agrave;ctics per a l&rsquo;elaboraci&oacute; de propostes.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" height=\"96\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/fons_uab_8_polaroid_1024x768.jpg\" width=\"171\" /></p>\n<p>\n	La Jornada estar&agrave; condu&iuml;da pel Dr. Juan Riese, Punt Nacional de Contacte de Salut (NCP), del Instituto de Salud Carlos III.</p>\n<p>\n	Podeu consultar el programa <a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/Programa%20catalaH2020.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n<p>\n	Si esteu interessats en assistir-hi, podeu fer-ho omplint el seg&uuml;ent <a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/investigar/itineraris/la-recerca/horizon-2020/jornada-informativa-9-de-juny-horizon-2020-repte-social-1-salut-1345685102586.html\" target=\"_blank\">formulari.</a></p>\n<p>\n	Al finalitzar la jornada,&nbsp; es podr&agrave; realitzar una entrevista personal amb el Dr. Juan Riese, si aix&iacute; s&rsquo;indica abans a la inscripci&oacute;.</p>\n<p>\n	La jornada es dur&agrave; a terme a la Facultat de Medicina</p>\n','9 de juny- Jornada informativa HORIZON 2020- Àrea de Salut','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-05-21','',0,NULL,0),(225,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Informaci&oacute;n sobre los diferentes t&oacute;picos a publicar el pr&oacute;ximo mes de septiembre, criterios de evaluaci&oacute;n y consejos pr&aacute;cticos para la elaboraci&oacute;n de propuestas.<br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" height=\"96\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/fons_uab_8_polaroid_1024x768.jpg\" width=\"171\" /></p>\n<p>\n	La Jornada estar&aacute; conducida por el Dr. Juan Riese, Punto Nacional de Contacto de Salud (NCP), del Instituto de Salud Carlos III.</p>\n<p>\n	Consultar el programa (catal&aacute;n)&nbsp; <a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/Programa%20catalaH2020.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n<p>\n	Si se est&aacute; interesado en asistir, rellenar el siguiente&nbsp; <a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/investigar/itineraris/la-recerca/horizon-2020/jornada-informativa-9-de-juny-horizon-2020-repte-social-1-salut-1345685102586.html\" target=\"_blank\">formulario.</a></p>\n<p>\n	Al finalizar la jornada, se podr&aacute; realizar una entrevista personal con el Dr. Juan Riese, si as&iacute; se indica antes en la inscripci&oacute;n.</p>\n<p>\n	La jornada se llevar&aacute; a cabo en la&nbsp; Facultat de Medicina.</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','9 de junio- Jornada informativa HORIZON 2020- Área de Salud','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-05-21','',0,NULL,1),(226,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Information about the various topics to publish next September, evaluation criteria and tips for preparing proposals.<br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" height=\"96\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/fons_uab_8_polaroid_1024x768.jpg\" width=\"171\" /></p>\n<p>\n	The conference will be led by Dr. Juan Riese, National Contact Point of Health (NCP), of the <em>Instituto de</em><em>Salud Carlos III</em>.</p>\n<p>\n	You can see the program (catalan)&nbsp; <a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/Programa%20catalaH2020.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></p>\n<p>\n	If you are interested to attend, you can do so by filling out the&nbsp; <a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/investigar/itineraris/la-recerca/horizon-2020/jornada-informativa-9-de-juny-horizon-2020-repte-social-1-salut-1345685102586.html\" target=\"_blank\">form.</a></p>\n<p>\n	At the end of the day, you can make a personal interview with Dr. Juan Riese, if is indicated in the registration.</p>\n<p>\n	The informative conference will be held at the Faculty of Medicine.</p>\n','June, 9th- Informative Conference HORIZON 2020- Health Area','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-05-21','',0,NULL,2),(227,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	El proper divendres 19 de juny, en el marc de la Jornada Doctoral del programa de Neuroci&egrave;ncies, visita l&rsquo;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies la <em><strong><a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/Meredith%20LeMasurier%20CV%20brief.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Dra. Meredith S. Le Masurier</span></a></strong></em>, editora en cap de la revista Nature Neuroscience. Le Masurier impartir&agrave; una conferencia on parlar&agrave; dels secrets per a publicar articles cient&iacute;fics de qualitat: <a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/MeredithLeMasurier.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong><em>The Insider&rsquo;s guide to scientific publishing.</em></strong></span></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/image004web.jpg\" style=\"width: 40%;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Durant la seva estada doctoral al laboratori de Chris Miller de la Universitat de Brandeis, Meredith LeMasurier va estudiar les propietats intr&iacute;nseques dels canals de potassi. Despr&eacute;s es va mudar a la &nbsp;<em>Oregon</em><em> Health and Science University</em> per la seva formaci&oacute; postdoctoral amb Peter Gillespie, centrant-se en la transducci&oacute; sensorial en els sistemes auditius i vestibulars. Abans d&#39;unir-se a la revista Nature Neuroscience en 2014, Meredith va ser l&#39;editora adjunta de la revista Neuron, on havia estat membre de l&#39;equip editorial des de 2007.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/NOU.gif\" style=\"width: 26px; height: 13px;\" /> Consulteu el programa de tota la Jornada amb modificacions <a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/ProgramaJornadaNeurocienciesV2.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">aqu&iacute;</span></a></p>\n','Jornada Doctoral Programa de Neurociències- Conferència Meredith S. Le Masurier','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-05-27','',0,NULL,0),(228,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	El pr&oacute;ximo viernes 19 de junio, en el marco de la Jornada Doctoral del programa de Neurociencias, visita el <em>Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</em> la&nbsp; <em><strong><a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/Meredith%20LeMasurier%20CV%20brief.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Dra. Meredith S. Le Masurier</span></a></strong></em>, editora en jefe de la revista Nature Neuroscience. Le Masurier impartir&aacute; una conferencia donde hablar&aacute; de los secretos para publicar art&iacute;culos cient&iacute;ficos de calidad: <a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/MeredithLeMasurier.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong><em>The Insider&rsquo;s guide to scientific publishing.</em></strong></span></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/image004web.jpg\" style=\"width: 40%;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Durante&nbsp; su estancia de doctorado en el laboratorio de Chris Miller en la Universidad &nbsp;de Brandeis, Meredith LeMasurier estudio las propiedades intr&iacute;nsecas de los canales de potasio. Despu&eacute;s se mud&oacute; a &nbsp;la &nbsp;<em>Oregon </em><em>Health and Science University</em> para su formaci&oacute;n postdoctoral con Peter Gillespie, centr&aacute;ndose en la transducci&oacute;n sensorial en los sistemas auditivos y vestibulares. Antes de unirse a la revista Nature Neuroscience en 2014, Meredith fue la editora adjunta de la revista Neuron, donde hab&iacute;a sido miembro del equipo editorial.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/NOU.gif\" style=\"width: 26px; height: 13px;\" /> Programa de la Jornada con modificaciones disponible<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/ProgramaJornadaNeurocienciesV2.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">aqu&iacute;</span></a></p>\n','Jornada Doctoral Programa de Neurociencias- Conferencia Meredith S. Le Masurier','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-05-27','',0,NULL,1),(229,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	On Friday 19<sup>th</sup> June as part of the Mid-term review public presentations PhD Program in Neuroscience, visits the &ldquo;<em>Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies&rdquo;</em>&nbsp; <em><strong><a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/Meredith%20LeMasurier%20CV%20brief.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Dr. Meredith S. Le Masurier</span></a></strong></em>, Chief editor of the journal Nature Neuroscience. Le Masurier will give a conference talk about the secrets about publishing scientific papers of quality:<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/MeredithLeMasurier.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong><em> The Insider&rsquo;s guide to scientific publishing.</em></strong></span></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/image004web.jpg\" style=\"width: 40%;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	During her doctoral work in the laboratory of Chris Miller at Brandeis University, Meredith Le Masurier studied the intrinsic properties of potassium channels. She then moved to Oregon Health and Science University for her postdoctoral training with Peter Gillespie, focusing on sensory transduction in the auditory and vestibular systems. Before joining&nbsp;Nature Neuroscience&nbsp;in 2014, Meredith was the Deputy Editor of Neuron, where she had been a member of the editorial team since 2007.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/NOU.gif\" style=\"width: 26px; height: 13px;\" /> Now you can check the full program with modifications&nbsp; <a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/files/ProgramaJornadaNeurocienciesV2.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">here</span></a></p>\n','Mid-term review public presentations PhD Program in Neuroscience- Meredith S. Le Masurier Conference','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-05-27','',0,NULL,2),(230,NULL,'<p>\n	L&rsquo;ICE coordina aquests cursos per a l&rsquo; aprenentatge i reciclatge del professorat , un cop finalitzat el curs acad&egrave;mic.</p>\n<p>\n	<a href=\"http://ice.uab.cat/estiu15/activitats.php#Cursos\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/ICE2015.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies estar&agrave; present en la nova edici&oacute;, amb el curs: <a href=\"http://ice.uab.cat/estiu15/CE1.php\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">El cervell. L&rsquo;&uacute;ltima frontera del coneixement</span></a><span style=\"color:#000000;\">.</span> &nbsp;Ja estan obertes les<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><a href=\"http://ice.uab.cat/estiu15/alta.php\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">inscripcions.</span></a><br />\n	<br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','L’Institut de Neurociències participa en una nova edició dels  cursos d’estiu del ICE ','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-05-29','',0,NULL,0),(231,NULL,'<p>\n	El ICE coordina estos &nbsp;cursos para el aprendizaje y reciclaje del profesorado, una vez finalizado el curso acad&eacute;mico.</p>\n<p>\n	<a href=\"http://ice.uab.cat/estiu15/activitats.php#Cursos\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/ICE2015.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	El Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies estar&aacute; presente en la nueva edici&oacute;n, con el curso: <a href=\"http://ice.uab.cat/estiu15/CE1.php\">El cerebro. La &uacute;ltima frontera del conocimiento</a>. Ya est&aacute;n abiertas las <a href=\"http://ice.uab.cat/estiu15/alta.php\" target=\"_blank\">inscripciones.</a></p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','El Institut de Neurociències participa en una nueva edición de los cursos de verano del  ICE','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-05-29','',0,NULL,1),(232,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	The ICE is coordinating the courses for learning and retraining of teachers, once the academic year is finished.</p>\n<p>\n	<a href=\"http://ice.uab.cat/estiu15/activitats.php#Cursos\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/ICE2015.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies will be presenting the new edition with the course:<a href=\"http://ice.uab.cat/estiu15/CE1.php\" target=\"_blank\"> The brain.The last frontier of knowledge.</a> <a href=\"http://ice.uab.cat/estiu15/alta.php\" target=\"_blank\">Registrations</a> are now open.</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','Institut de Neurociències  participates  in a new edition of the summer courses of ICE','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-05-29','',0,NULL,2),(233,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Dins del fort comprom&iacute;s que t&eacute; l&rsquo;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies amb la doc&egrave;ncia, per aquest proper curs acad&egrave;mic es presenten nous reptes.<br />\n	L&rsquo;INc consta a les bases de dades per rebre alumnes en pr&agrave;ctiques del&nbsp; <a href=\"http://www.idec.upf.edu/master-en-comunicacio-cientifica-medica-i-ambiental\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>M&agrave;ster en Comunicaci&oacute; Cient&iacute;fica, M&egrave;dica i Ambiental de la UPF</strong></a> i del <a href=\"http://www.ub.edu/biblio/grau-dinformacio-i-documentacio/practicum.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Grau d&#39;Informaci&oacute; i Documentaci&oacute; de la UB</strong></a>. Tanmateix, pel proper curs acad&egrave;mic s&#39;ha signat un conveni per acollir alumnes en pr&agrave;ctiques dels <a href=\"http://mmpol.cat/index.php/estudis-superior/cicles-formatius-superior/grau-superior-gral\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Cicles Formatius de Grau Superior, de l&#39;Institut Miquel Mart&iacute; i Pol</strong></a>, de Cornell&agrave; de Llobregat.</p>\n<p>\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/cervellDocencia.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','Nous reptes docents de l\'INc','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-06-10','',1,NULL,0),(234,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Dentro del fuerte compromiso que tiene el <em>Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</em> con la docencia, para este pr&oacute;ximo curso acad&eacute;mico se presentan nuevos retos.<br />\n	El INc consta en las bases de datos para recibir alumnos en pr&aacute;cticas del &nbsp; <strong><a href=\"http://www.idec.upf.edu/master-en-comunicacion-cientifica-medica-y-ambiental\" target=\"_blank\">M&aacute;ster en Comunicaci&oacute;n Cient&iacute;fica, M&eacute;dica y Ambiental de la UPF</a></strong> y del <strong><a href=\"http://www.ub.edu/biblio/introduccion/breve-presentacion-en-espanol-2.html\">Grado de Informaci&oacute;n y Documentaci&oacute;n de la UB</a></strong>. Asimismo, el pr&oacute;ximo curso acad&eacute;mico se ha firmado un convenio para acoger alumnos en pr&aacute;cticas de los <a href=\"http://mmpol.cat/index.php/estudis-superior/cicles-formatius-superior/grau-superior-gral\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Ciclos Formativos de Grado Superior del Instituto Miquel Mart&iacute; i Pol</strong>,</a> de <em>Cornell&agrave; de Llobregat.</em></p>\n<p>\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/cervellDocencia.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></p>\n','Nuevos retos docentes del INc','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-06-10','',1,NULL,1),(235,NULL,'<p>\n	Within the strong commitment of <em>Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</em> with teaching, for this coming academic year presents new challenges.<br />\n	The INc figure in databases for trainees of the&nbsp; <a href=\"http://www.idec.upf.edu/master-in-scientific-medical-and-environmental-communication\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Master in Scientific, Medical and Environmental Communication-UPF</strong></a><strong> </strong>and also for the <a href=\"http://www.ub.edu/biblio/introduccio/versio-anglesa.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Degree of Information and Documentation- UB</strong></a>. Also, the next academic year has signed an agreement to host trainees of <strong><a href=\"http://mmpol.cat/index.php/estudis-superior/cicles-formatius-superior/grau-superior-gral\" target=\"_blank\">Upper Grade Educational Cycle of <em>Institut Miquel Mart&iacute; i Pol</em> </a></strong>in <em>Cornell&agrave; de Llobregat</em>.</p>\n<p>\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/cervellDocencia.JPG\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></p>\n','INc, new teaching challenges','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-06-10','',1,NULL,2),(236,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	El grup de Recerca de la Dra Mercedes Unzeta, ha signat conjuntament amb el&nbsp; grup del&nbsp; Dr. Joan Muntaner (VHIR) &nbsp;un conveni de col&middot;laboraci&oacute; internacional amb l&rsquo;empresa japonesa R-Tech Ueno.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/MUnzeta.jpg\" style=\"width: 50%;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	L&rsquo;objectiu es col&middot;laborar amb l&rsquo;empresa per provar el seu f&agrave;rmac RTU-009 (inhibidor de l&rsquo;enzim VAP-1) combinat amb t-PA (anticoagulant) en models animals d&rsquo;infart cerebral i valorar el seu potencial per iniciar assajos cl&iacute;nics.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	El <a href=\"http://index.php#!/Mercedes UNZETA_291_1 \" target=\"_blank\">grup de la Dra. Mercedes Unzeta</a>, es expert en l&rsquo;estudi de SSAO/VAP-1 en la disfunci&oacute; neurovascular i la seva implicaci&oacute; en el Stroke, entre d&rsquo;altres.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Consulteu altres notes de premsa que fan referencia a aquesta not&iacute;cia:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/sala-de-premsa/detall-de-noticia/col-laboracio-internacional-de-la-uab-i-el-vhir-per-al-tractament-de-l-8217-infart-cerebral-1345667174054.html?noticiaid=1345686475372\" target=\"_blank\">-UAB</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.vhir.org/salapremsa/noticies/noticies_detall.asp?any=2015&amp;num=105&amp;mv1=5&amp;mv2=3&amp;Idioma=ca\" target=\"_blank\">-VHIR</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.rtechueno.com/en/investor/press/documents/150608_pr_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">-R-TECH UENO</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.bioportfolio.com/news/article/2358649/R-Tech-Ueno-Announcement-on-Collaborative-Development-of-Therapeutic-Agent-for-Cerebral.html\" target=\"_blank\">-BIOPORTFOLIO</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','Acord de col.laboració INc- VHIR i l’empresa japonesa R-Tech Ueno per al tractament de l’infart cerebral','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-06-10','',0,NULL,0),(237,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	El grupo de Investigaci&oacute;n de la Dra Mercedes Unzeta, ha firmado conjuntamente con el grupo del Dr. Joan Muntaner (VHIR) un convenio de colaboraci&oacute;n internacional con la empresa japonesa R-Tech Ueno.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/MUnzeta.jpg\" style=\"width: 50%;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	El objetivo es colaborar con la empresa para probar su f&aacute;rmaco RTU-009 (inhibidor de la enzima VAP-1) combinado con t-PA (anticoagulante) en modelos animales de infarto cerebral y valorar su potencial para iniciar ensayos cl&iacute;nicos.<br />\n	<br />\n	El <a href=\"http://index.php#!/Mercedes Unzeta_470_1 \" target=\"_blank\">grupo de la Dra. Mercedes Unzeta</a>, es experto en el estudio de SSAO / VAP-1 en la disfunci&oacute;n neurovascular y su implicaci&oacute;n en el Stroke, entre otros.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Consulta de otras notas de prensa que hacen referencia a esta not&iacute;cia:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/sala-de-premsa/detall-de-noticia/col-laboracio-internacional-de-la-uab-i-el-vhir-per-al-tractament-de-l-8217-infart-cerebral-1345667174054.html?noticiaid=1345686475372\" target=\"_blank\">-UAB</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.vhir.org/salapremsa/noticies/noticies_detall.asp?any=2015&amp;num=105&amp;mv1=5&amp;mv2=3&amp;Idioma=ca\" target=\"_blank\">-VHIR</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.rtechueno.com/en/investor/press/documents/150608_pr_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">-R-TECH UENO</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.bioportfolio.com/news/article/2358649/R-Tech-Ueno-Announcement-on-Collaborative-Development-of-Therapeutic-Agent-for-Cerebral.html\" target=\"_blank\">-BIOPORTFOLIO</a></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','Acuerdo de colaboración INc-VHIR y la empresa japonesa R-Tech Ueno para el tratamiento del infarto cerebral.','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-06-10','',0,NULL,1),(238,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	The research group of Dr. Mercedes Unzeta has signed together with the group of Dr. Joan Muntaner (VHIR) an international &nbsp;collaboration agreement with the Japanese company R-Tech Ueno.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Pagines/MUnzeta.jpg\" style=\"width: 50%;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	The goal is to work with the company to test its drug RTU-009 (inhibitor of the enzyme VAP-1) combined with t-PA (anticoagulant) in animal models of Stroke and assess its potential initiating clinical trials.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	The <a href=\"http://index.php#!/Mercedes Unzeta_437_1 \" target=\"_blank\">group of Dr. Mercedes Unzeta</a> is expert in the study of SSAO / VAP-1 neurovascular dysfunction and its involvement in the Stroke, among others.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">Check other</span> <span class=\"hps\">press releases</span> <span class=\"hps\">that refer to</span> <span class=\"hps\">this article:</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/newsroom/news-detail-1345668003610.html?noticiaid=1345686475372\" target=\"_blank\">-UAB</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.vhir.org/salapremsa/noticies/noticies_detall.asp?Idioma=en&amp;mv1=5&amp;mv2=3&amp;mh1=0&amp;mh2=0&amp;mh3=0&amp;mh4=0&amp;ms=0&amp;any=2015&amp;num=105\" target=\"_blank\">-VHIR</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.rtechueno.com/en/investor/press/documents/150608_pr_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">-R-TECH UENO</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.bioportfolio.com/news/article/2358649/R-Tech-Ueno-Announcement-on-Collaborative-Development-of-Therapeutic-Agent-for-Cerebral.html\" target=\"_blank\">-BIOPORTFOLIO</a></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','Collaboration agreement INc-VHIR and the Japanese company R-Tech Ueno for the treatment of Stroke.','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-06-10','',0,NULL,2),(239,NULL,'<p>\n	Ja est&agrave; oberta la <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/research/participants/portal4/desktop/en/opportunities/h2020/calls/h2020-msca-if-2015.html\" target=\"_blank\">convocat&ograve;ria Marie S. Curie</a> d&#39;enguany, on l&#39;INc, amb tots els seus grups de recerca representats, figura com instituci&oacute; d&#39;acollida.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/mariecurieactions.jpg\" style=\"width: 225px; height: 225px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n	Per&nbsp; a m&eacute;s informaci&oacute;, podeu consultar la nostra secci&oacute; d&#39;<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Catala/index.php#!/Convocat%C3%B2ries%20obertes_670_1\">ofertes de treball.</a></p>\n','L\'Institut de Neurociències, centre d\'acollida per a beques Marie S. Curie','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-06-16','',0,NULL,0),(240,NULL,'<p>\n	Ya est&aacute; abierta la <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/research/participants/portal4/desktop/en/opportunities/h2020/calls/h2020-msca-if-2015.html\" target=\"_blank\">convocatoria Marie S. Curie 2015</a>, donde el INc, con todos los grupos de investigaci&oacute;n representados, figura como instituci&oacute;n de acogida.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/mariecurieactions.jpg\" style=\"width: 225px; height: 225px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n	Para m&aacute;s informaci&oacute;n, consultar la <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Castellano/index.php#!/Convocatorias%20abiertas_671_1\">secci&oacute;n de ofertas de trabajo.</a></p>\n','El Institut de Neurociències, centro de acogida para becas Marie S. Curie','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-06-16','',0,NULL,1),(241,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Now the call <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/research/participants/portal4/desktop/en/opportunities/h2020/calls/h2020-msca-if-2015.html\" target=\"_blank\">Marie S. Curie 2015 </a>is opened; this time the INc., with all the research groups represented, appears as a hosting institution.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/mariecurieactions.jpg\" style=\"width: 225px; height: 225px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n	For further information, you can see our<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/English/index.php#!/Open%20calls_672_1\"> job opportunities section.</a></p>\n','The Institut de Neurociències, hosting institution for Marie S. Curie fellows','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-06-16','',0,NULL,2),(242,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/150629_IMARIS%20web_CAT.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><br />\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/Logo-IMARIS-8web.jpg\" style=\"width: 20%;\" /></span></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"inc.uab.cat/Catala/index.php#!/Microsc%C3%B2pia_231_1\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">El Servei de microsc&ograve;pia del Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</span></a>, ja disposa del programa IMARIS, software especialitzat en la gesti&oacute; de dades de la imatge, els seus protocols d&rsquo;an&agrave;lisi, resultats i m&eacute;s dades derivades. L&rsquo;eina ja la podeu trobar operativa al mateix servei.</p>\n<p>\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/DSC00938web.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','Software IMARIS ja disponible a l\' INc','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-06-30','',0,NULL,0),(243,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/150629_IMARIS%20web_SP.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><br />\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/Logo-IMARIS-8web.jpg\" style=\"width: 20%;\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Castellano/index.php#!/Microscop%C3%ADa_368_1\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">El Servicio de Microscopia del<em> Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</em></span></a>, ya dispone del programa IMARIS, software especializado en la gesti&oacute;n de datos de la imagen, sus protocolos de an&aacute;lisis, resultados y m&aacute;s datos derivados. La herramienta ya se puede encontrar operativa en el mismo servicio.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/DSC00938web.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></p>\n','Software IMARIS ya disponible en el INc','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-06-30','',1,NULL,1),(244,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/150629_IMARIS%20web_EN.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><br />\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/Logo-IMARIS-8web.jpg\" style=\"width: 20%;\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/English/index.php#!/Microscope%20Unit_360_1\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">The <em>Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies&nbsp;</em> Microscopy unit</span></a>, already has the Imaris program, specializing in the management of image data software, protocols analysis, results and derived data. The tool can now be found operating in the same service.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/DSC00938web.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','Software IMARIS available now at INc','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-06-30','',1,NULL,2),(245,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Ahir es va fer entrega dels premis ICREA al recinte modernista de l&rsquo;Hospital de Sant Pau; amb la Dra. Roser Nadal com a una de les guardonades amb la modalitat &ldquo;Acad&egrave;mia&rdquo;.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/icreaRNadal.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/icreaRNadal.jpg\" style=\"width: 70%;\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Podeu llegir la nota de premsa UAB <a href=\"http://bit.ly/1R71fKI\" target=\"_blank\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n','Entrega premis ICREA','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-07-02','',0,NULL,0),(246,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Ayer se hizo entrega de los premios ICREA en el recinto modernista del Hospital de Sant Pau; con la Dra. Roser Nadal como una de las galardonadas en la modalidad &ldquo;Academia&rdquo;.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/icreaRNadal.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/icreaRNadal.jpg\" style=\"width: 70%;\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	Nota de prensa UAB disponible <a href=\"http://bit.ly/1KzQNGl\" target=\"_blank\">aqu&iacute;</a></p>\n','Entrega premios ICREA','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-07-02','',0,NULL,1),(247,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Yesterday were handed out the ICREA awards in the modernist grounds of Hospital de Sant Pau; with Dra. Roser Nadal as one of the recipients in the modality &quot;Academy&quot;.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/icreaRNadal.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/icreaRNadal.jpg\" style=\"width: 70%;\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n	UAB press release (spanish) available <a href=\"http://bit.ly/1KzQNGl\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></p>\n','ICREA awards','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-07-02','',0,NULL,2),(248,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Un estudi internacional, coordinat pel Dr. <a href=\"http://inc.uab.cat/Catala/profile.php?id=88\">Rub&eacute;n L&oacute;pez </a>de l&#39;Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies &nbsp;identifica una diana terap&egrave;utica per al tractament de lesions medul&middot;lars agudes. La recerca, publicada a <em>The Journal of Neuroscience</em>, mostra com l&#39;administraci&oacute; d&#39;un f&agrave;rmac incrementa la mobilitat en ratolins que han patit una lesi&oacute; medul&middot;lar.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.jneurosci.org/content/35/28/10224.short\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/cover Jneurosci.gif\" style=\"width: 45%;\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/sala-de-premsa/detall-de-noticia/identifiquen-una-diana-terapeutica-per-tractar-lesions-medul-lars-1345667174054.html?noticiaid=1345688440569\" target=\"_blank\">Nota de premsa UAB</a></p>\n','Identifiquen una diana terapèutica per tractar lesions medul.lars','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-07-16','',0,NULL,0),(249,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	Un estudio internacional, coordinado por el Dr. <a href=\"inc.uab.cat/Castellano/profile.php?id=88\">Rub&eacute;n L&oacute;pez</a> del <em>Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</em> identifica una diana terap&eacute;utica para el tratamiento de lesiones medulares agudas. La investigaci&oacute;n, publicada en <em>The Journal of Neuroscience</em>, muestra como la administraci&oacute;n de un f&aacute;rmaco incrementa la movilidad en ratones tras una lesi&oacute;n medular.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.jneurosci.org/content/35/28/10224.short\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/cover Jneurosci.gif\" style=\"width: 45%;\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/sala-de-prensa/detalle-noticia-1345667994339.html?noticiaid=1345688440569\" target=\"_blank\">Nota de prensa UAB</a></p>\n','Identifican una diana terapéutica para tratar lesiones medulares','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-07-16','',0,NULL,1),(250,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	An International study, coordinated by the <em>Institut de Neuroci&egrave;ncies</em> researcher, Dr. <a href=\"inc.uab.cat/English/profile.php?id=88\">Ruben Lopez </a>identifies a therapeutic target for the treatment of acute spinal cord injuries. According to this research, published in the <em>Journal of Neuroscience</em>, the administration of a drug increases the mobility of mice that have suffered a spinal cord injury.</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.jneurosci.org/content/35/28/10224.short\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/cover Jneurosci.gif\" style=\"width: 45%;\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.uab.cat/web/newsroom/news-detail-1345668003610.html?noticiaid=1345688440569\" target=\"_blank\">UAB press release</a></p>\n','Therapeutic target identified for treatment of spinal cord injuries','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-07-16','',0,NULL,2),(251,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	L&rsquo;exposici&oacute; de quadres &ldquo;Cells On Canvas&rdquo; del Dr. Carlos Barcia i les creacions en joieria &ldquo;Neurojewelry&rdquo; del Dr. Bernardo Castellano, han format part, entre d&rsquo;altres, d&rsquo;una mostra d&rsquo;art que s&rsquo;ha organitzat en el context del&nbsp; XII European Meeting on Glial Cells in Health and Disease, celebrat &nbsp;del 15 al 18 de juliol.</p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n				<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/GlioArtGral.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/GlioArtGral.jpg\" style=\"width: 90%;\" /></a></td>\n			<td>\n				<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/GlioArtCB1.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/GlioArtCB1.jpg\" style=\"width: 90%;\" /></a></td>\n			<td>\n				<a href=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/GlioArtBC1.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/DocsCKeditor/images/Noticies/GlioArtBC1.jpg\" style=\"width: 110%;\" /></a></td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n','Glio-Art Exhibition: Mostra d\'art al congrès sobre Glia de Bilbao','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','2015-07-21','',0,NULL,0),(252,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n	La exposici&oacute;n de cuadros &quot;Cells On Canvas&quot; del Dr. Carlos Barcia y las cr